(3, '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', 'hypnotherapy-67x67.jpg', 'SJB WELLBEING', '<p>SJB wellbeing is a healing practice founded by Sharon Bland&nbsp;a Dubai-based British expert in Spiritual Trance Healing and Tibetan Usui Reiki.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sharon offers:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tibetan Usui Traditional Reiki&nbsp;</strong>(Offering healing sessions and Reiki Workshops)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Neuro Solution Orientated Kineseology&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;(Offering private sessions in balancing mind body and spirit)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Clinical Hypnotherapy&nbsp;</strong>(offering hypnotherapy for self empowerment of ones life and taking charge. Also hypnotherapy for addictions, fears &amp; Phobias)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT)</strong>&nbsp;(Healing sessions and workshops available in releasing old and unwanted emotions to facilitate to the core issue)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Access Cons</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Releasing old beliefs, patterns,behaviours and judgements)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ciousness Bars&nbsp;</strong>(Practitioner and Facilitator offering healing sessions and workshops to become a certified Access Bars Practitioner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Reflexology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kineseology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Crystal healing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chakra balancing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Jin Shin Jyutsu&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>For more information please call +971</strong>506847410 or send an email to&nbsp;</strong><strong><a href=\"mailto:sharon@sjbewellbeing.com\" target=\"_blank\">sharon@sjbewellbeing.com</a>. You can also visit the website at &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"http://www.sjbwellbeing.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>www.sjbwellbeing.com</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:500px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Email Address</strong></td>\r\n			<td>sharon@sjbewellbeing.com</td>\r\n		<