(56, 'girl-face-leaf_sm.jpg', 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'KALM HOLISTIC BEAUTY, PALM JUMEIRAH', '<p>A one-stop holistic shop offering women facials, manicures, pedicures, eyelash<br />\r\nextensions, massages, waxing, threading, hair treatments, haircut and blow drying.<br />\r\nA holistic beauty place where women can relax and pamper themselves with products that contain natural ingredients (botanical, essential oils, fruit extracts,&hellip;).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Palm Island Jumeira, Riva Beach Club, between Shoreline Apartments 7 and 8.<br />\r\nTel: +971 4 451 9988<br />\r\nwww.kalmbeauty.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@kalmbeauty.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 4 451 9988</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Palm Island Jumeira, Riva Beach Club, between Shoreline Apartments 7 and 8</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '10'),
(57, 'girl-face-leaf_sm.jpg', 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'TALISE WELLNESS SPA, MADINAT JUMEIRAH', '<p>Blending integrative medicine and diagnostics with holistic therapies, Talise Spa offers a variety of different massage, body treatments and facials using the ultimate in spa products. Features 26 treatment rooms, including couples suites and a variety of facials, massages and body treatments using top range spa products.<br />\r\nRelax in any of the relaxation areas consisting of private male and female changing rooms equipped with sauna, steam and plunge pools. The spa also features a communal swimming pool which serves a variety of health conscious spa cuisine. Facilities also include our own private yoga studio which caters to group and personal sessions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Daily Sunset Yoga</strong><br />\r\nEnd the day right at Talise Spa Madinat Jumeirah&rsquo;s ultimate outdoor sunset yoga experience with unrivalled views of the Arabian Gulf and the iconic Burj Al Arab.<br />\r\nDaily Sunset Yoga Sessions at Al Qasr beach from 17:30 starting 1 October 2013<br />\r\nAll levels welcome</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Full moon yoga on the beach</strong><br />\r\n<em>Upcoming Full Moon Dates &amp; Time for 2013 and 2014</em><br />\r\nSaturday, 19 October 2013 at 19:30<br />\r\nSunday, 17 November 2013 at 19:30<br />\r\nTuesday, 17 December 2013 at 19:30<br />\r\nThursday, 16 January 2014 at 19:30<br />\r\nSaturday, 15 February 2014 at 19:30<br />\r\nSunday, 16 March 2014 at 19:30<br />\r\nTuesday, 15 April 2014 at 19:30<br />\r\nWednesday, 14 May 2014 at 19:30<br />\r\nFriday, 13 June 2014 at 19:30</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel. +971 4 366 6818<br />\r\nEmail: MJtalise@jumeirah.com<br />\r\nwww.jumeirah.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>MJtalise@jumeirah.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 4 366 6818</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '10'),
