(60, 'girl-face-leaf_sm.jpg', 'web_organic_food.jpg', 'ORGANIC FOODS AND CAFÃ‰', '<p>Organic Foods and Caf&eacute; is a family run organic supermarket and caf&eacute; chain that sells fresh organic and biodynamic food, supplements, skincare, cosmetics, baby items and household cleaning products. The brand has outlets in the Greens, Jumeirah and Sheikh Zayed Road. They also do home deliveries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;We opened our first store in Satwa, Dubai in 2004. Organic Foods and Cafe currently supplies over 10,000 hormone and chemical free products direct from family run farms throughout the world.<br />\r\n&ldquo;We do not buy from the open market, nor from traders. We have a selection of handpicked farmers whom we have personally visited (and regularly pay a visit to) and who have the same values we do:<br />\r\n&ldquo;Thomas and Brigitte Eberharter produce the finest goats cheese for us; Sue from Wensleydale ensures we always get the freshest fruits; our friends at Saraaketha in Sri Lanka who have visited us countless times also help us have the best fruit and veg. We value our suppliers and their family values.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CONTACTS</strong><br />\r\nGeneral enquiries: 04 338 2911<br />\r\nFor deliveries only : 050 240 4405<br />\r\nYou can contact OFC from Saturday to Thursday from 8am til 8pm.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For online orders:<br />\r\nhomedelivery@organicfoodsandcafe.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For general enquiries:<br />\r\ncustomerservice@organicfoodsandcafe.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For marketing and press enquiries:<br />\r\nmarketing@organicfoodsandcafe.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>www.organicfoodsandcafe.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>customerservice@organicfoodsandcafe.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 338 2911</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.organicfoodsandcafe.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '10'),
(61, 'girl-face-leaf_sm.jpg', 'web_beauty.jpg', 'SISTERS BEAUTY LOUNGE', '<p>Soothing treatments for women &ndash; massages, facials, scrubs, hair removal, reflexology, manicures and pedicures, slimming treatments, hammam, spray tan, bridal make up, eyelash and eyebrow treatments&hellip; to name some of the services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sisters Beauty Lounge carries products from The Organic Pharmacy, a leading British brand reputed to be the first and only pharmacy in the world dedicated to organic health and beauty. TOP is known for its luxurious treatments using its own specially-formulated all-natural products.<br />\r\nSisters is offering The Organic Pharmacy&rsquo;s four signature treatments, namely:<br />\r\nRose Crystal Lymphatic Facial for re-energised, glowing skin;<br />\r\nVitamin C &amp; Papaya Enzyme Peel Facial, which brightens the skin by targeting pigmentation and uneven spots;<br />\r\nSolution Facial for Combination Skin, deep-cleansing facial that leaves your skin fresh and revitalized; and,<br />\r\nBack Detox Facial, aimed at removing congestion and leave you with a smooth, deeply cleansed back.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sisters Beauty Lounge&nbsp;is located in five locations throughout the country: Al Bateen in Abu Dhabi, The Village Mall in Jumeirah, The Dubai Mall, Mirdif City Centre, and the Mall of the Emirates.&nbsp; Opening soon will be the sixth Sisters Beauty Lounge branch located in St. Regis Hotel in Abu Dhabi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@sistersbeautylounge.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 3398500</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Al Bateen in Abu Dhabi, The Village Mall in Jumeirah, The Dubai Mall, Mirdif City Centre, and the Mall of the Emirates. Opening soon will be the sixth Sisters Beauty Lounge branch located in St. Regis Hotel in Abu Dhabi. www.sistersbeautylounge.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '10'),
