(64, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_detox.jpg', 'THE WELLNESS BROTHERS', '<p>Sean and Ryan Penny are the Wellness Brothers.&nbsp;Originally from South Africa, they each hold a Masters Degree Homeopathy from the University of Johannesburg. In 2005, they relocated to Dubai with their families.<br />\r\nServices and programs include DNA testing for health, diet and fitness; the ABC of fat-loss; 10 or 15 day detox plans, and more.<br />\r\nThe wellness mission of the brothers is &nbsp;to provide effective health, weight, and performance solutions to individuals, groups, and companies. They aim to do this through<em><strong>&nbsp;</strong></em>seven individual goals:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Move more (often)</li>\r\n	<li>Eat better</li>\r\n	<li>Perform well</li>\r\n	<li>Lose weight</li>\r\n	<li>Quit smoking</li>\r\n	<li>Stress less</li>\r\n	<li>Sleep soundly</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ABOUT SEAN PENNY:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Homeopathic Practitioner &ndash; M.Tech.Hom. (SA) (Registered in SA and licensed in Dubai)</li>\r\n	<li>Homotoxicologist</li>\r\n	<li>Certified Personal Trainer</li>\r\n	<li>Co-author &ndash; something BIGGER and NO SWEAT</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>RYAN PENNY:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Homeopathic Practitioner &ndash; M. Tech. Hom. (SA) (Registered in SA)</li>\r\n	<li>Homotoxicologist</li>\r\n	<li>Clinical Nutritionist &ndash; DCN</li>\r\n	<li>Certified Personal Trainer</li>\r\n	<li>Co-author &ndash; something BIGGER and NO SWEAT</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>contactus@thewellnessbrothers.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 441 9687 to book an appt with Ryan at Optimal Fitness in Studio City, Dubai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.thewellnessbrothers.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '11'),
(65, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'TRIBEFIT GYM & CLUB', '<p><strong>TribeFit</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; is about &lsquo;<strong>Social Fitness</strong>&lsquo;, i.e., getting fit and connecting with people in a funked-out space that is not just a gym but a Club with a caf&eacute; and lounge all rolled into one.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Besides a world-class Gym, Group Exercise classes, access to a range of team Sports facilities, inspirational Personal Training, &nbsp;Beach Bootcamps, and in-club DJs, TribeFit also has a packed Social Calendar with activities like monthly Parties, Brunches, Coffee Mornings and Evenings, Movie Nights, Networking Events, outdoor Camping Trips and more, designed to get members mixing and talking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Work out, get introduced, create friendships, meet people, or even fall in love with people who have a common interest in fitness, socially active living, and having fun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All you have to do is show up, plug in and play. The Tribe takes care of the rest.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Call the Tribe on&nbsp;<strong>800 TRIBE (87423)</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If it matters to you, it matters to us. Email us on<strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@tribefit.com\">info@tribefit.com</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Silverene Tower in Dubai Marina.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Directions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Silverene Tower is located right next to Dubai Marina Mall (when driving in the direction from Dubai to Abu Dhabi). TribeFit is on the entire Mezzanine and Ground floor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TribeFit is above Carrefour Supermarket. You can also access TribeFit from Marina Walk.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>http://www.tribefit.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@tribefit.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>800 TRIBE (87423)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Silverene Tower in Dubai Marina</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '11'),
(66, 'web_green-car.jpg', 'web_green-car.jpg', 'GREEN CAR RENTAL', '<p>A range of hybrid to 100 per cent electric vehicles to hire. From the Nissan Leaf to the BMW X6 Hybrid and Tesla Roadster. Tel. 04 321 7478. Email: info@ greencardubai.com www.greencardubai.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@greencardubai.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 321 74</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.greencardubai.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '12'),
(67, 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'SJB WELLBEING', '<p>SJB wellbeing is a healing practice founded by Sharon Bland&nbsp;a Dubai-based British expert in Spiritual Trance Healing and Tibetan Usui Reiki.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sharon offers:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tibetan Usui Traditional Reiki&nbsp;</strong>(Offering healing sessions and Reiki Workshops)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Neuro Solution Orientated Kineseology&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;(Offering private sessions in balancing mind body and spirit)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Clinical Hypnotherapy&nbsp;</strong>(offering hypnotherapy for self empowerment of ones life and taking charge. Also hypnotherapy for addictions, fears &amp; Phobias)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT)</strong>&nbsp;(Healing sessions and workshops available in releasing old and unwanted emotions to facilitate to the core issue)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Access Consciousness Bars&nbsp;</strong>(Practitioner and Facilitator offering healing sessions and workshops to become a certified Access Bars Practitioner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Releasing old beliefs, patterns,behaviours and judgements)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Reflexology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kineseology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Crystal healing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chakra balancing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Jin Shin Jyutsu&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>For more information please call +971</strong></strong><strong>506847410 or send an email to&nbsp;</strong><strong><a href=\"mailto:sharon@sjbewellbeing.com\" target=\"_blank\">sharon@sjbewellbeing.com</a>. You can also visit the website at &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"http://www.sjbwellbeing.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>www.sjbwellbeing.com</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>sharon@sjbewellbeing.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971506847410</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address