(82, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'RACHEL FOY HYPNOTHERAPY', '<p>Hypnotherapy, NLP Coaching, Personal Development &amp; Life Coaching, Private Consultations, Corporate bookings &amp; Group Workshops.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rachel provides you with tools, strategies and techniques to help you improve your life physically, mentally or emotionally. &ldquo;Maybe you are wanting to become a non-smoker or perhaps break free from food related issues, diets and counting calories.&nbsp; Or maybe you are wanting more self confidence and to be in control of your emotions, behaviour and thoughts. Or maybe you are wanting a different approach to a health condition.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rachel Foy BSc (Hons) MLCHom Dip Hyp MBIH<br />\r\nClinical &amp; Cognitive Behavioral Hypnotherapist<br />\r\nCorporate Wellness Coach</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Call the DUBAI clinic for a FREE assessment session on 04-4503525</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Located in the heart of JLT, Cluster V.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.rachelfoy.com/\">www.rachelfoy.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Check Out Rachel&rsquo;s Other Websites:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hypnobanddubai.com/\">www.hypnobanddubai.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.dubaiweightloss.com/\">www.dubaiweightloss.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.rachelfoystopsmoking.com/\">www.rachelfoystopsmoking.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hypnobirthdubai.com/\">www.hypnobirthdubai.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://ww.hypertensiondubai.com/\">ww.hypertensiondubai.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@rachelfoy.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>04-4503525</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.rachelfoy.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '18'),
(83, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'web_counselling.jpg', 'TRANSFORMATIONS INSTITUTE', '<p>Using NLP, the Transformations team help clients increase their productivity, work and learn smarter, improve memory and concentration, resolve problems creatively, and enjoy greater confidence and self-esteem.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By combining theory and practice, revealing powerful self-awareness techniques and using state-of-the-art technologies, the TI team demonstrate how to think in open mode, stimulate and apply imagination, harness creative energy, master new skills and make the key choices necessary to transform the quality of your life and achieve your vision of success and well being. Courses include the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Individual Coaching, Counselling &amp; Therapy</li>\r\n	<li>Couples, Marital &amp; Relationship Counselling</li>\r\n	<li>Hypnobirthing</li>\r\n	<li>Parent Education &amp; Family Therapy</li>\r\n	<li>Emotional Freedom Techniques (EFT)</li>\r\n	<li>Neuro-Linguistic Programming (NLP)</li>\r\n	<li>Life &amp; Career Makeovers</li>\r\n	<li>Professional Practitioner Therapist Trainings</li>\r\n	<li>Continuing Professional Development: short courses</li>\r\n	<li>Corporate Consultancy &amp; Training</li>\r\n	<li>Stop Smoking</li>\r\n	<li>Certificate in Satir Model Counselling for Individuals, Couples &amp; Family Therapy</li>\r\n	<li>Satir Transformational Systemic Therapy &amp; Conjoint Family Therapy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>http://transforminst.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@transforminst.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 4 344 0115</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>http://transforminst.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '18'),
(84, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'SJB WELLBEING', '<p>SJB wellbeing is a healing practice founded by Sharon Bland&nbsp;a Dubai-based British expert in Spiritual Trance Healing and Tibetan Usui Reiki.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sharon offers:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tibetan Usui Traditional Reiki&nbsp;</strong>(Offering healing sessions and Reiki Workshops)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Neuro Solution Orientated Kineseology&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;(Offering private sessions in balancing mind body and spirit)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Clinical Hypnotherapy&nbsp;</strong>(offering hypnotherapy for self empowerment of ones life and taking charge. Also hypnotherapy for addictions, fears &amp; Phobias)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT)</strong>&nbsp;(Healing sessions and workshops available in releasing old and unwanted emotions to facilitate to the core issue)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Access Consciousness Bars&nbsp;</strong>(Practitioner and Facilitator offering healing sessions and workshops to become a certified Access Bars Practitioner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Releasing old beliefs, patterns,behaviours and judgements)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Reflexology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kineseology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Crystal healing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chakra balancing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Jin Shin Jyutsu&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>For more information please call +971</strong></strong><strong>506847410 or send an email to&nbsp;</strong><strong><a href=\"mailto:sharon@sjbewellbeing.com\" target=\"_blank\">sharon@sjbewellbeing.com</a>. You can also visit the website at &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"http://www.sjbwellbeing.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>www.sjbwellbeing.com</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>sharon@sjbewellbeing.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971506847410</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address<