(98, 'angelic-presence-1200-x-900-e1422018227863.jpg', 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'AWAKENED SOUL, RACHEL BEAVAN', '<p>A healer and psychotherapist, Rachel offers courses in Metaphysics including Mediumship Development, Intuitive Development, Usui Reiki Healing, Meditation and Spiritual Healing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>She also offers one on one healing using a mix of the following modalities: Trance Communication, N.F.N.L.P Hypnotherapist, Past Life Regression, Spiritual Regression, N.L.P., Reiki, Spiritual Healing</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: beavanrachel@mac.com www.rachelbeavan.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>beavanrachel@mac.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>0000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.rachelbeavan.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '19'),
