(102, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'THE CHIRON CLINIC', '<p>A&nbsp;complementary and alternative medical clinic, the Chiron Clinic treats the &lsquo;whole&rsquo; individual, and addresses causative factors of illness, and focuses on optimizing functionality and prevention of disease.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Services on&nbsp;offer include anthropsophical medicine, homeopathy, clinical nutrition, herbal medicines, acupuncture and Traditional Chinese Medicine (see below), spinal alignment, counseling/coaching, hydrotherapy, detoxification, and infrared-sauna therapy, to treat a wide array of family health concerns including; eczema and other skin complaints, autism/ADHD, anxiety/depression, digestive complaints, hormonal issues, migraine/tension head-aches, insomnia, allergies, low immunity, ear infections, asthma, and joint &amp; back pain. We also offer allergy screening, and a wide array of functional testing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dr. Lanalle and Dr. Amel are both North-American Board Certified Naturopathic Doctors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>From AED&nbsp;</em>300/session<br />\r\n<em>Open Saturday-Thursday 8:30-8:30.</em><br />\r\n<em>160 2D St. Al Bada&rsquo;a/Jumeirah 1 (Behind Life Pharmacy)&nbsp;</em><br />\r\n<em>Tel. 04 349 7444</em><br />\r\n<em>Email: info@thechironclinic.com</em><br />\r\n<em>www.facebook.com/TheChironClinic</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Acupuncture</strong><br />\r\nThe Chiron Clinic offers Traditional Chinese Medicine treatments including acupuncture, Chinese herbals and cupping.<br />\r\nDr. Wang Ping specializes in fertility, hormonal &amp; pregnancy complaints, musculoskeletal injuries, and stress.<br />\r\nThe Chiron Clinic also offers treatments for weight loss, detoxification, allergy screens &amp; desensitization, anxiety, depression, gastrointestinal complaints, skin problems, using natural &amp; complementary medicine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>From AED 300/session</em><br />\r\n<em>Open Saturday-Thursday 8:30-8:30.</em><br />\r\n<em>160 2D St. Al Bada&rsquo;a/Jumeirah 1 (Behind Life Pharmacy), Dubai, UAE</em><br />\r\n<em>Tel. 04 349 7444</em><br />\r\n<em>Email: info@thechironclinic.com</em><br />\r\n<em>www.facebook.com/TheChironClinic</em></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@thechironclinic.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 349 7444</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>160 2D St. Al Bada&rsquo;a/Jumeirah 1 (Behind Life Pharmacy)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '20'),
(103, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'web_detox.jpg', 'THE WELLNESS BROTHERS', '<p>Sean and Ryan Penny are the Wellness Brothers.&nbsp;Originally from South Africa, they each hold a Masters Degree Homeopathy from the University of Johannesburg. In 2005, they relocated to Dubai with their families.<br />\r\nServices and programs include DNA testing for health, diet and fitness; the ABC of fat-loss; 10 or 15 day detox plans, and more.<br />\r\nThe wellness mission of the brothers is &nbsp;to provide effective health, weight, and performance solutions to individuals, groups, and companies. They aim to do this through<em><strong>&nbsp;</strong></em>seven individual goals:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Move more (often)</li>\r\n	<li>Eat better</li>\r\n	<li>Perform well</li>\r\n	<li>Lose weight</li>\r\n	<li>Quit smoking</li>\r\n	<li>Stress less</li>\r\n	<li>Sleep soundly</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ABOUT SEAN PENNY:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Homeopathic Practitioner &ndash; M.Tech.Hom. (SA) (Registered in SA and licensed in Dubai)</li>\r\n	<li>Homotoxicologist</li>\r\n	<li>Certified Personal Trainer</li>\r\n	<li>Co-author &ndash; something BIGGER and NO SWEAT</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>RYAN PENNY:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Homeopathic Practitioner &ndash; M. Tech. Hom. (SA) (Registered in SA)</li>\r\n	<li>Homotoxicologist</li>\r\n	<li>Clinical Nutritionist &ndash; DCN</li>\r\n	<li>Certified Personal Trainer</li>\r\n	<li>Co-author &ndash; something BIGGER and NO SWEAT</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>contactus@thewellnessbrothers.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 441 9687 to book an appt with Ryan at Optimal Fitness in Studio City, Dubai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.thewellnessbrothers.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '20'),
(104, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'web_energy-healing.jpg', 'GEMS OF YOGA', '<p>A team of yoga instructors from different parts of India impart yoga education in different styles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A team comprising a Naturopathy Doctor, Ayurvedic Doctor and a Dietician along with male and female Ayurveda therapists provide a complete programme for body, mind and soul.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suite 1701, White Crown Building,&nbsp;Sheikh Zayed Road<br />\r\nTel: 04 3315161, 055 6532750<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/gemsofyoga\">www.facebook.com/gemsofyoga</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.gemsofyogadubai.com/\">www.gemsofyogadubai.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>gemsofyoga@live.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 331 5161</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Suite 1701, White Crown Building, between Royal Radisson Hotel &amp; Crown Plaza Hotel, Sheikh Zayed Road</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '20'),
(105, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'HEAVEN ON EARTH MED SPA', '<p>Heaven on Earth Med Spa offers&nbsp;Holistic Massage, Organic Essential Oil Aromatherapy and Hamam, Naturopathic and Natural Wellness Consultations, as well as Organic Living Foods Weight Loss &amp; Reversing Diabetes programmes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Natural Health and Wellness Consultation &ndash; AED 400 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nConsultation with Celeste Michele Roberts, American Board Certified Traditional Naturopath, Wellness and Spa Director. Learn easy ways through diet, fitness, and stress management to super charge your health and wellness. Specialty programs for: Reversing Diabetes Naturally, Weight Loss, Optimal Health and Wellness and Peak Performance in Sports Performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Private Fitness Training &ndash; AED 250 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nTrain with one of our physiotherapist in our gym to improve range of motion and performance, this training wth the physiotherapist is idea for athletes recovering from any injuries or for the person just starting on a fitness regime to ensure proper techniques in gym training and ensure safety. Private yoga, pilates, martial arts Capoeira, and fitness for pregnancy training courses also available.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Physiotherapy / Physical Therapy &ndash; AED 495 &ndash; 90 min or AED 395 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nOur expert physiotherapists will work with you to help you with your ability to move, reduce pain, restore function, and prevent disability. A wide variety of conditions are treated within this service, from low back pain to frozen shoulder, neck problems, slipped disc problems, and from headaches to ankle sprains, and knee problems. Physiotherapy can be an alternative to surgery or used to benefit before after surgeries when they are necessary for faster healing. Some specialities of our physiotherapists include: Cyriax Method, Pilates, Reflexology, Therapeutic Medical Massage, and Sports.<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.heavenonearthmedspa.com/\">www.HeavenOnEarthMedSpa.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>celeste@holistichealthonline.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0) 4 454 2806</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Concord Tower #2102, Dubai Media City, On Beach Rd. Opposite the Palm Jumeirah</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '20'),
(106, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'vegetable-garden.jpg', 'AGRICULTURE BOX', '<p>Grow your own fruit, vegetables and herbs and enjoy nourishing food with maximum nutrition for you and you family. Agriculture Box provides produce at your fingertips. Agriculture Box is supplied with everything you need to start growing. Soil, seeds, irrigation/drainage, composting system, organic fertiliser solution, installation and delivery, we provide a turn key solution for your convenience. Low maintenance and easy to use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Comes in a natural wood finish. Agriculture Box has longevity and will last a long time due to the European kiln dried white wood. Our British and European certified food graded waterproofing system inside the box forbids any volatile organic compound (VOC) transfers and offers safe and durable protection for the box.Agriculture Boxes are installed in homes, schools and palaces across the UAE.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: +971 52 875 1318<br />\r\nEmail:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:agriculturebox@gmail.com\">agriculturebox@gmail.com</a><br />\r\nAl Jawharah Building, Suite 104, Khalid Bin Waleed Road<br />\r\nP.O Box: 27971, Dubai<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.agriculturebox.com/\">www.agriculturebox.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>agriculturebox@gmail.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 52 875 1318</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.agriculturebox.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '20'),
(107, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'blue-planet-green-people--e1385232417321.jpg', 'BLUE PLANET GREEN PEOPLE', '<p>Blue Planet Green People (BPGP) is the first organic and natural retail store in JLT. BPGP provides organic and eco-home care, life style products, body care, organic gourmet meals, health foods, along with fruit and veggie produce from local producers. There is also a farmer&rsquo;s market on Fridays between 11 am until 3 pm .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information please call 0097143695209 or email info@bpgpuae.com.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also visit the website www.<a href=\"http://blueplanetgreenpeople.com/\">blueplanetgreenpeople.com</a>&nbsp;and order online .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>BPGP is located in Jumeirah Lakes Towers, BS4 ,&nbsp;Al Seef 2, Cluster U, Dubai.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@bpgpuae.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>0097143695209</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Jumeirah Lakes Towers, BS4 , Al Seef 2, Cluster U, Dubai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '20'),
(108, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'green-e1385219266899.jpg', 'GREENHEART ORGANIC FARMS', '<p>Freshly harvested organic produce from UAE farms sold to Dubai residents, via designated collection points or through home delivery ( minimun order Dh100). All the produce on offer is chemical and pesticide-free. The farms practise bio diversity, crop rotation and companion planting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information or ordering please call 056 6407060 or send an email to&nbsp;elena@greenheartuae.com .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can pop in to the shop in The Light Building,&nbsp;Ground Floor, Shop 8,&nbsp;Arjan, Al Barsha 2, Dubai.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>An online ordering system is also in place, just visit the website&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.greenheartuae.com/\">www.greenheartuae.com</a>&nbsp;and order online.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>elena@greenheartuae.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>056 6407060</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.greenheartuae.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '20'),
