(118, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'web_detox.jpg', 'GENERATION NOURISHED', '<p>Holistic Health Coaching programmes for women and teenagers looking to lose weight, gain energy, have blood sugar imbalance, or want to overhaul their diet &amp; lifestyle.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Deepti Bhatia is a holistic health coach and creator of Generation Nourished a.k.a Gen N. She coaches clients from teenagers, brides-to-be as well, as mums, on how to reach their goals for energy, resolve disordered eating, stress reduction and increase vitality. Find Gen N on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GenerationNourished\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GenerationNourished\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/GenerationNourished</a>&nbsp;and visit:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.generationnourished.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.GenerationNourished.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: 055 106 7511 www.generationnourished.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@generationnourished.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)55 106 7511</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.generationnourished.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '20'),
