(125, 'blue-planet-green-people--e1385232417321.jpg', 'thumb_GJB-232.jpg', 'GREEN BAGS UAE', '<p>Green Bags UAE is the first company who introduces the concept of eco-friendly bags in UAE. It&rsquo;s the leading provider of jute ,cotton and juco bags. These ethically-produced reusable bags are an ecologically-friendly replacement for plastic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;According to the customer&rsquo;s preference, we bring out bags in different colors, style and sizes. Whatever is your requirement, bulk or small quantity, our production unit takes care of all your needs with utmost precision &rdquo; .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel. 04 370 5277</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:enquiry@greenbagsuae.com\">enquiry@greenbagsuae.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>www.greenbagsuae.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>enquiry@greenbagsuae.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>04 370 5277</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.greenbagsuae.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '22');
