(126, 'blue-planet-green-people--e1385232417321.jpg', 'web_organic_food.jpg', 'ORGANIC FOODS AND CAFÃ‰', '<p>Organic Foods and Caf&eacute; is a family run organic supermarket and caf&eacute; chain that sells fresh organic and biodynamic food, supplements, skincare, cosmetics, baby items and household cleaning products. The brand has outlets in the Greens, Jumeirah and Sheikh Zayed Road. They also do home deliveries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;We opened our first store in Satwa, Dubai in 2004. Organic Foods and Cafe currently supplies over 10,000 hormone and chemical free products direct from family run farms throughout the world.<br />\r\n&ldquo;We do not buy from the open market, nor from traders. We have a selection of handpicked farmers whom we have personally visited (and regularly pay a visit to) and who have the same values we do:<br />\r\n&ldquo;Thomas and Brigitte Eberharter produce the finest goats cheese for us; Sue from Wensleydale ensures we always get the freshest fruits; our friends at Saraaketha in Sri Lanka who have visited us countless times also help us have the best fruit and veg. We value our suppliers and their family values.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CONTACTS</strong><br />\r\nGeneral enquiries: 04 338 2911<br />\r\nFor deliveries only : 050 240 4405<br />\r\nYou can contact OFC from Saturday to Thursday from 8am til 8pm.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For online orders:<br />\r\nhomedelivery@organicfoodsandcafe.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For general enquiries:<br />\r\ncustomerservice@organicfoodsandcafe.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For marketing and press enquiries:<br />\r\nmarketing@organicfoodsandcafe.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>www.organicfoodsandcafe.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>customerservice@organicfoodsandcafe.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 338 2911</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.organicfoodsandcafe.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '