(153, 'vegetable-garden.jpg', 'vegetable-garden.jpg', 'AGRICULTURE BOX', '<p>Grow your own fruit, vegetables and herbs and enjoy nourishing food with maximum nutrition for you and you family. Agriculture Box provides produce at your fingertips. Agriculture Box is supplied with everything you need to start growing. Soil, seeds, irrigation/drainage, composting system, organic fertiliser solution, installation and delivery, we provide a turn key solution for your convenience. Low maintenance and easy to use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Comes in a natural wood finish. Agriculture Box has longevity and will last a long time due to the European kiln dried white wood. Our British and European certified food graded waterproofing system inside the box forbids any volatile organic compound (VOC) transfers and offers safe and durable protection for the box.Agriculture Boxes are installed in homes, schools and palaces across the UAE.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: +971 52 875 1318<br />\r\nEmail:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:agriculturebox@gmail.com\">agriculturebox@gmail.com</a><br />\r\nAl Jawharah Building, Suite 104, Khalid Bin Waleed Road<br />\r\nP.O Box: 27971, Dubai<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.agriculturebox.com/\">www.agriculturebox.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>agriculturebox@gmail.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 52 875 1318</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.agriculturebox.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '30'),
(154, 'vegetable-garden.jpg', 'blue-planet-green-people--e1385232417321.jpg', '', '<p>Blue Planet Green People (BPGP) is the first organic and natural retail store in JLT. BPGP provides organic and eco-home care, life style products, body care, organic gourmet meals, health foods, along with fruit and veggie produce from local producers. There is also a farmer&rsquo;s market on Fridays between 11 am until 3 pm .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information please call 0097143695209 or email info@bpgpuae.com.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also visit the website www.<a href=\"http://blueplanetgreenpeople.com/\">blueplanetgreenpeople.com</a>&nbsp;and order online .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>BPGP is located in Jumeirah Lakes Towers, BS4 ,&nbsp;Al Seef 2, Cluster U, Dubai.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@bpgpuae.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>0097143695209</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Jumeirah Lakes Towers, BS4 , Al Seef 2, Cluster U, Dubai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '30'),
(155, 'vegetable-garden.jpg', 'green-e1385219266899.jpg', 'GREENHEART ORGANIC FARMS', '<p>Freshly harvested organic produce from UAE farms sold to Dubai residents, via designated collection points or through home delivery ( minimun order Dh100). All the produce on offer is chemical and pesticide-free. The farms practise bio diversity, crop rotation and companion planting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information or ordering please call 056 6407060 or send an email to&nbsp;elena@greenheartuae.com .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can pop in to the shop in The Light Building,&nbsp;Ground Floor, Shop 8,&nbsp;Arjan, Al Barsha 2, Dubai.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>An online ordering system is also in place, just visit the website&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.greenheartuae.com/\">www.greenheartuae.com</a>&nbsp;and order online.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>elena@greenheartuae.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>056 6407060</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.greenheartuae.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '30'),
(156, 'vegetable-garden.jpg', 'balqees-honey-e1384864744238.jpg', 'BALQEES HONEY', '<p>Raw Yemeni Sidr Honey is the best and most expensive in the world due to taste, nutritional and medicinal value. &nbsp;The shop is located in Dubai Mall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For free delivery around Dubai please call 04 325 0666 /&nbsp;0506552023 or email to&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@balqees.com\">info@balqees.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also visit the website at&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.balqees.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.balqees.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@balqees.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>04 325 0666</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.balqees.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '30'),
(157, 'vegetable-garden.jpg', 'web_organic_food.jpg', 'BAKER & SPICE', '<p>Salads, handmade wild bread, cakes, breakfasts and mains, all made from locally sourced ingredients where possible. Location: Souk al Bahar and Dukkan al Manzil, Downtown Dubai. Marina Promenade. Maps on website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Our philosophy &ndash; local, organic, fresh and homemade &ndash; is a benchmark for excellence. The menu represents an exciting daily journey through the farms and markets of the UAE and the region, constantly changing with the seasons and availability of fresh locally grown and mainly organic ingredients. We offer diners an expeience with food in its purest and freshest form.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Baker &amp; Spice &ndash; Souk Al Bahar<br />\r\nP.O. BOX 116593, Dubai, UAE<br />\r\nP: +971 4 4252240<br />\r\nF: +971 4 4252241<br />\r\nE: soukalbahar@bakerandspiceme.com<br />\r\ninfo@bakerandspiceme.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Baker &amp; Spice &ndash; Dukkan Al Manzil<br />\r\nP.O. BOX 116593, Dubai, UAE<br />\r\nP: +971 4 4279856<br />\r\nF: +971 4 4279855<br />\r\nE: almanzil@bakerandspiceme.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Baker &amp; Spice &ndash; Marina Promenade<br />\r\nP.O. BOX 116593, Dubai, UAE<br />\r\nP: +971 4 3624686<br />\r\nF: +971 4 3624772<br />\r\nE: marina@bakerandspiceme.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>www.bakerandspiceme.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@bakerandspiceme.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 425 2240</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.bakerandspiceme.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '30'),
(158, 'vegetable-garden.jpg', 'web_organic_food.jpg', 'ORGANIC FOODS AND CAFÃ‰', '<p>Organic Foods and Caf&eacute; is a family run organic supermarket and caf&eacute; chain that sells fresh organic and biodynamic food, supplements, skincare, cosmetics, baby items and household cleaning products. The brand has outlets in the Greens, Jumeirah and Sheikh Zayed Road. They also do home deliveries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;We opened our first store in Satwa, Dubai in 2004. Organic Foods and Cafe currently supplies over 10,000 hormone and chemical free products direct from family run farms throughout the world.<br />\r\n&ldquo;We do not buy from the open market, nor from traders. We have a selection of handpicked farmers whom we have personally visited (and regularly pay a visit to) and who have the same values we do:<br />\r\n&ldquo;Thomas and Brigitte Eberharter produce the finest goats cheese for us; Sue from Wensleydale ensures we always get the freshest fruits; our friends at Saraaketha in Sri Lanka who have visited us countless times also help us have the best fruit and veg. We value our suppliers and their family values.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CONTACTS</strong><br />\r\nGeneral enquiries: 04 338 2911<br />\r\nFor deliveries only : 050 240 4405<br />\r\nYou can contact OFC from Saturday to Thursday from 8am til 8pm.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For online orders:<br />\r\nhomedelivery@organicfoodsandcafe.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For general enquiries:<br />\r\ncustomerservice@organicfoodsandcafe.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For marketing and press enquiries:<br />\r\nmarketing@organicfoodsandcafe.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>www.organicfoodsandcafe.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>customerservice@organicfoodsandcafe.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 338 2911</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.organicfoodsandcafe.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '30'),
(159, 'web_meditation.jpg', 'web_meditation.jpg', 'ZARINE DADACHANJI', '<p>Zarine Dadachanji holds gong bath meditations as well as guided meditations at various times and locations around Dubai.<br />\r\nFor more information, go to www.meetup.com/Gong Bath Meditation-Dubai</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>zarine_d@hotmail.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)50 650 9954</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.meetup.com/Gong Bath Meditation-Dubai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '31'),
(160, 'web_meditation.jpg', 'web_holistic-ctrs.jpg', 'THE THIRD EYE CENTRE', '<p>A holistic wellness centre with branches in Dubai and Manila</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hypnotherapy &amp; EFT</strong><br />\r\nClinical Hypnotherapist Monisha specialises in EFT and Hypnotherapy. Offers workshops such as Taking Charge, Self Hypnosis, Karma and Forgiveness. Contact Monisha at The Third Eye Centre.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Feng shui</strong><br />\r\nEnergy clearing and space management for corporates and individuals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gong Bath Meditations with Lawrence Ender</strong>le<br />\r\nLawrence hosts Gong Bath Meditations and Sound and Vibration sessions and workshops.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1101 Saeed Tower II<br />\r\nOn top of Nandos/KFC<br />\r\nNext to Four Points Sheraton<br />\r\nSheikh Zayed Road<br />\r\nEmail: info@thirdeyeonline.com<br />\r\nTel: 04 326 6539<br />\r\nwww.thirdeyeonline.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@thirdeyeonline.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 326 6539</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>1101 Saeed Tower II, www.thirdeyeonline.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '31'),
(161, 'web_meditation.jpg', 'flame-of-mindfulness2.jpg', 'ASPEN AMAN, THE GONG HOUSE', '<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>aspen@thegonghouse.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>0508733545</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.meetup.com/the-gong-house</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '31'),
(162, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'IGNITE FITNESS & WELLNESS', '<p>Ignite Fitness and Wellness offer a range of fitness and wellness solutions, including military bootcamps, personal training, innovative group exercise, corporate wellness, life coaching, personal styling and nutritional advice for the individual, neighbourhood and business communities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ignite&rsquo;s Group Ex classes are guaranteed to get you stretching, lifting, toning, dancing, boxing and strengthening your way to better health and fitness. With a wide variety of styles and levels of intensity there&rsquo;s something for everyone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Classes are held throughout Dubai in all Ignite gymnasiums including the Riva Beach Club on the Palm Jumeirah, Park Place on Sheikh Zayed Road and The Shack in Umm Sequim.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Group Ex classes include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Box-Fit</li>\r\n	<li>Fit-yoga</li>\r\n	<li>ZUMBA</li>\r\n	<li>Girls Only</li>\r\n	<li>Circuits</li>\r\n	<li>Bootcamp Overhaul</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>CONTACTS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>General / Switchboard &ndash; call (+9714) 4562482 or email info@ignite-wellness.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Military Bootcamp &amp; Group Exercise &ndash; call Fabian on 055 736 4669 or email fabian@ignite-wellness.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Personal Training &ndash; call Fabian on 055 736 4669 or email fabian@ignite-wellness.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sponsorship, PR, Marketing Liz 050 104 2338 or email liz@ignite-wellness.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Corporate Wellness &ndash; call Guillaume on 050 715 0785 or email guillaume@ignite-wellness.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ignite Sport Services, Warehouse No 1, Al Manara Street, Po Box 454844, Dubai, UAE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[t]: +971 (0)4 456 2482 [f]:+971 (0)4 452 2555</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@ignite-wellness.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971(0)4) 456 2482</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.ignite-wellness.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '32');
