(182, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'web_holistic-ctrs.jpg', 'THE MIRACLES CENTER', '<p>Miracles, is not only a holistic well being center, it is also a community that thrives to help transform the lives of people of all age groups in life. We believe that with the usage and practice of the therapies and techniques offered here, that you can change your life for the better NOW! We have a team of highly qualified and experienced therapists and facilitators that offer a variety of alternative therapy techniques assisting you in overcoming the stress of this fast paced life that we all live in.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our community of therapists and healers are here to assist you in bringing out the best within you, equipping you with the tools to accomplish your dreams in life, and make miracles happen everywhere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Icon Tower, office 306, next to Byblos Hotel Tecom (Dubai Internet City Metro) Tel: 056 148 5118 Email: info@miraclesworldwide.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@miraclesworldwide.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)56 148 5118</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Icon Tower, office 306, next to Byblos Hotel Tecom (Dubai Internet City Metro). www.miraclesworldwide.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '36'),
(183, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'web_holistic-ctrs.jpg', 'THE THIRD EYE CENTRE', '<p>A holistic wellness centre with branches in Dubai and Manila</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hypnotherapy &amp; EFT</strong><br />\r\nClinical Hypnotherapist Monisha specialises in EFT and Hypnotherapy. Offers workshops such as Taking Charge, Self Hypnosis, Karma and Forgiveness. Contact Monisha at The Third Eye Centre.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Feng shui</strong><br />\r\nEnergy clearing and space management for corporates and individuals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gong Bath Meditations with Lawrence Ender</strong>le<br />\r\nLawrence hosts Gong Bath Meditations and Sound and Vibration sessions and workshops.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1101 Saeed Tower II<br />\r\nOn top of Nandos/KFC<br />\r\nNext to Four Points Sheraton<br />\r\nSheikh Zayed Road<br />\r\nEmail: info@thirdeyeonline.com<br />\r\nTel: 04 326 6539<br />\r\nwww.thirdeyeonline.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@thirdeyeonline.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 326 6539</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>1101 Saeed Tower II, www.thirdeyeonline.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '36'),
(184, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'web_holistic-ctrs.jpg', 'ILLUMINATIONS WELL-BEING CENTRE', '<p>Illuminations is a Dubai-based well-being centre inspiring individuals towards a journey of self-discovery as a key to lasting happiness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Illuminations offers a variety of services based on a holistic approach to self-development. The intention is to provide a deeper insight into the mind-body-energy connection influencing our experience of life. As a result, individuals feel more balanced and complete within themselves.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Illuminations provides the following services for individuals, corporate professionals and young adults to avail from:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&bull;Daily meditations</li>\r\n	<li>&bull;Self-empowerment workshops &amp; Seminars</li>\r\n	<li>&bull;Holistic training programs</li>\r\n	<li>&bull;Private consultations</li>\r\n	<li>&bull;Holistic products</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>THERAPISTS</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Lukas Putz</strong><br />\r\nAn Spiritual Response Therapy (SRT) practitioner and teacher, Lukas offers private healing sessions, meditations and classes for those wanting to learn SRT or Spiritual Restructuring (SpR).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CAREER TRAINING</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Integrated Clinical Hypnotherapy</strong><br />\r\nIlluminations Well-Being Centre is certified by the Universal School of Integrated Clinical Hypnotherapy Middle East. Five stages. For more information, go to www.usich-me.com or call Illuminations on 04 448 7043.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Office 409, Fortune Executive Towers, Cluster T, Plot T1, JLT (next to Dubai Marina Metro</em>).</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>admin@illuminationsworld.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 448 7043</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.illuminationsworld.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '36'),
(185, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'web_holistic-ctrs.jpg', 'THE HOLISTIC INSTITUTE', '<p>A variety of holistic therapies, studies and career training.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Resident and guest practitioners offer hypnotherapy (Rachel Foy), magnetic therapy, Jin Shin Jyutsu, feng shui, and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Holistic Institute is IFPA and ITEC accredited for diplomas in Clinical Aromatherapy and Reflexology.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@theholisticinsitute.org</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 450 3535</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.theholisticinstitute.org</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '36'),
(186, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'aromatherapy1.jpg', 'SPADUNYA CLUB', '<p>Award-winning holistic and wellness spa for women using the 100 per cent organic, French colour therapy spa range called Altearah Bio in holistic vibrational and energetic treatments. Hammam, hydrotherapy, beauty room and steam, sauna and showers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Holistic Wellness Consultants offer therapies that include Reflexology, Iridology, Holistic Nutrition, Theta Healing, Quantum Reading, the Dorn Method, PIDDDS (Personal Integrated Dynamics, Diet and Determination), Breuss Massage, and Reiki.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fitness@Spadunya<br />\r\nSpadunya Club&rsquo;s fitness centre offers Personal Training, Aerobics, Pilates, Yoga, Dance, kids classes and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Therapists working out of SpaDunya Club include:<br />\r\nStephanie Niazi: Stephanie uses iridology to evaluates wellness imbalances through tissue markings in the eyes which are addressed with holistic nutrition and food solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Karima Nanji: A Dorn Method therapist, Karima offers treatment for back pain and issues stemming from the spine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shams 1, The Walk at JBR, Plaza Level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@spadunyaclub.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 439 3669</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.spadunyaclub.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '36'),
(187, 'web_detox.jpg', 'web_detox.jpg', 'THE WELLNESS BROTHERS', '<p>Sean and Ryan Penny are the Wellness Brothers.&nbsp;Originally from South Africa, they each hold a Masters Degree Homeopathy from the University of Johannesburg. In 2005, they relocated to Dubai with their families.<br />\r\nServices and programs include DNA testing for health, diet and fitness; the ABC of fat-loss; 10 or 15 day detox plans, and more.<br />\r\nThe wellness mission of the brothers is &nbsp;to provide effective health, weight, and performance solutions to individuals, groups, and companies. They aim to do this through<em><strong>&nbsp;</strong></em>seven individual goals:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Move more (often)</li>\r\n	<li>Eat better</li>\r\n	<li>Perform well</li>\r\n	<li>Lose weight</li>\r\n	<li>Quit smoking</li>\r\n	<li>Stress less</li>\r\n	<li>Sleep soundly</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ABOUT SEAN PENNY:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Homeopathic Practitioner &ndash; M.Tech.Hom. (SA) (Registered in SA and licensed in Dubai)</li>\r\n	<li>Homotoxicologist</li>\r\n	<li>Certified Personal Trainer</li>\r\n	<li>Co-author &ndash; something BIGGER and NO SWEAT</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>RYAN PENNY:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Homeopathic Practitioner &ndash; M. Tech. Hom. (SA) (Registered in SA)</li>\r\n	<li>Homotoxicologist</li>\r\n	<li>Clinical Nutritionist &ndash; DCN</li>\r\n	<li>Certified Personal Trainer</li>\r\n	<li>Co-author &ndash; something BIGGER and NO SWEAT</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>contactus@thewellnessbrothers.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 441 9687 to book an appt with Ryan at Optimal Fitness in Studio City, Dubai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.thewellnessbrothers.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '37'),
(188, 'web_detox.jpg', 'web_spinal_therapy.jpg', 'OSTEOPATHIC HEALTH CENTRE', '<p>Malcolm Gregory, Nargis Raza and their team of therapists, give self-help and support to people suffering from pain.<br />\r\nIssues that the Osteopathic Health Centre (OHC) can help with include back pain, neck pain, headaches, frozen shoulder, sports injuries, RSI, sinusitis, whiplash, pregnancy care, trapped nerves, tennis elbow, growing pains, postural correction, correct breathing techniques, arthritic pain, pelvic pain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Treatments include ante natal care, homeopathy, hydrotherapy, osteopathy, psychology. OHC offers rehabilitation for post-orthopedic surgery, post cardiac surgery, back pain, neck pain, post natal, sports injury, post hemiplegia (stroke)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umm Suqueim and Mirdif</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: clinicsinfo@osteopathydubai.com<br />\r\nTel: 04 348 73 66<br />\r\nwww.osteopathydubai.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>clinicsinfo@osteopathydubai.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 348 73 66</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.osteopathydubai.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '37'),
