(231, 'Listings_leaves-and-water.jpg', 'web_beauty.jpg', 'HEAVEN ON EARTH MED SPA', '<p>Heaven on Earth Med Spa offers&nbsp;Holistic Massage, Organic Essential Oil Aromatherapy and Hamam, Naturopathic and Natural Wellness Consultations, as well as Organic Living Foods Weight Loss &amp; Reversing Diabetes programmes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Natural Health and Wellness Consultation &ndash; AED 400 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nConsultation with Celeste Michele Roberts, American Board Certified Traditional Naturopath, Wellness and Spa Director. Learn easy ways through diet, fitness, and stress management to super charge your health and wellness. Specialty programs for: Reversing Diabetes Naturally, Weight Loss, Optimal Health and Wellness and Peak Performance in Sports Performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Private Fitness Training &ndash; AED 250 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nTrain with one of our physiotherapist in our gym to improve range of motion and performance, this training wth the physiotherapist is idea for athletes recovering from any injuries or for the person just starting on a fitness regime to ensure proper techniques in gym training and ensure safety. Private yoga, pilates, martial arts Capoeira, and fitness for pregnancy training courses also available.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Physiotherapy / Physical Therapy &ndash; AED 495 &ndash; 90 min or AED 395 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nOur expert physiotherapists will work with you to help you with your ability to move, reduce pain, restore function, and prevent disability. A wide variety of conditions are treated within this service, from low back pain to frozen shoulder, neck problems, slipped disc problems, and from headaches to ankle sprains, and knee problems. Physiotherapy can be an alternative to surgery or used to benefit before after surgeries when they are necessary for faster healing. Some specialities of our physiotherapists include: Cyriax Method, Pilates, Reflexology, Therapeutic Medical Massage, and Sports.<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.heavenonearthmedspa.com/\">www.HeavenOnEarthMedSpa.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>celeste@holistichealthonline.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0) 4 454 2806</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Concord Tower #2102, Dubai Media City, On Beach Rd. Opposite the Palm Jumeirah</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '43'),
(232, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_beauty.jpg', 'GOLDâ€™S GYM LADIES SPA', '<p>Facial services, nail services, body massage and beauty services like manicure, pedicure, threading, Thai massage, slimming massage, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Two Dubai locations,&nbsp;Etihad Mall Ladies Club &amp; Spa. Tel. +971 (0)4 255 9882, email:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:reception_etl@goldsgyminternational.com\">reception_etl@goldsgyminternational.com</a>&nbsp;and Al Barsha Ladies Club &amp; Spa, Al Barsha Mall. Tel: +971 (0)4 385 1181, email:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:reception_abl@goldsgyminternational.com\" target=\"_blank\">reception_abl@goldsgyminternational.com</a>&nbsp;or call 800 GOLDS (46537)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.goldsgym.ae/\">www.goldsgym.ae</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>reception_etl@goldsgyminternational.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 255 9882</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Etihad Mall Ladies Club &amp; Spa</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '43'),
(233, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'REMÃˆDE SPA AT THE ST. REGIS ABU DHABI', '<p>One of UAE&rsquo;s largest spas at 3,000 square metres, the Rem&egrave;de Spa at The St. Regis Abu Dhabi offers 25 different bespoke facials, massages, body treatments, and spa packages for both ladies and gentlemen given by highly trained masseurs and aestheticians. Rem&egrave;de Spa is also the first in the UAE to offer real Oxyceutical&reg;therapies where pure oxygen is infused into the treatment to drive visible results.<br />\r\nExclusive to The St. Regis Hotels and Resorts, Rem&egrave;de Spas are found in New York, Singapore and Bali.<br />\r\nThe Rem&egrave;de Spa at The St. Regis Abu Dhabi features 11 private treatment rooms, each decorated with natural materials and earth tones as well as candles with rich aromas, plush throws, wooden floors and hand-crafted tile mosaics. The treatment rooms, wet areas, relaxation lounges and other amenities are available separately for ladies and gentlemen.<br />\r\nFor Rem&egrave;de Spa reservations, call (+971) 2 694 4758 or email remede.abudhabi@starwoodhotels.com.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>remede.abudhabi@starwoodhotels.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>(+971) 2 694 4758</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.stregisabudhabi.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '43'),
