(235, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'SIX SENSES SPA, ZIGHY BAY, OMAN', '<p>Intelligent luxury at this stunning resort that offers holistic wellness and pampering combining east and west therapies.? Located on the northern Musandam Peninsula in the Sultanate of Oman.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: +968 2 6735 555<br />\r\nwww.sixsenses.com/sixsenseszighybay</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>enquiries-spa@sixsenses.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+968 2 6735 555</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.sixsenses.com/sixsenseszighybay</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '43'),
(236, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'TALISE WELLNESS SPA, MADINAT JUMEIRAH', '<p>Blending integrative medicine and diagnostics with holistic therapies, Talise Spa offers a variety of different massage, body treatments and facials using the ultimate in spa products. Features 26 treatment rooms, including couples suites and a variety of facials, massages and body treatments using top range spa products.<br />\r\nRelax in any of the relaxation areas consisting of private male and female changing rooms equipped with sauna, steam and plunge pools. The spa also features a communal swimming pool which serves a variety of health conscious spa cuisine. Facilities also include our own private yoga studio which caters to group and personal sessions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Daily Sunset Yoga</strong><br />\r\nEnd the day right at Talise Spa Madinat Jumeirah&rsquo;s ultimate outdoor sunset yoga experience with unrivalled views of the Arabian Gulf and the iconic Burj Al Arab.<br />\r\nDaily Sunset Yoga Sessions at Al Qasr beach from 17:30 starting 1 October 2013<br />\r\nAll levels welcome</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Full moon yoga on the beach</strong><br />\r\n<em>Upcoming Full Moon Dates &amp; Time for 2013 and 2014</em><br />\r\nSaturday, 19 October 2013 at 19:30<br />\r\nSunday, 17 November 2013 at 19:30<br />\r\nTuesday, 17 December 2013 at 19:30<br />\r\nThursday, 16 January 2014 at 19:30<br />\r\nSaturday, 15 February 2014 at 19:30<br />\r\nSunday, 16 March 2014 at 19:30<br />\r\nTuesday, 15 April 2014 at 19:30<br />\r\nWednesday, 14 May 2014 at 19:30<br />\r\nFriday, 13 June 2014 at 19:30</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel. +971 4 366 6818<br />\r\nEmail: MJtalise@jumeirah.com<br />\r\nwww.jumeirah.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>MJtalise@jumeirah.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 4 366 6818</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '43'),
(237, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'LOTUS WELLNESS SPA', '<p>Holistic treatments for men and women.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lotus Hotel Apartments &amp; Spa, Dubai Marina<br />\r\nTel: +971 (0)4 440 2805<br />\r\nEmail: spa@lotus-hospitality.com<br />\r\nwww.lotus-hospitality.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>spa@lotus-hospitality.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 440 2805</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Lotus Hotel Apartments &amp; Spa, Dubai Marina</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '43'),
(238, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'NATURAL HEALING SPA', '<p>Inspired by traditional healing philosophies from China and Thailand, Natural Healing Spa embraces a holistic approach to physical and spiritual vitality.<br />\r\nLocated at the corner of Al Wasl Road, Natural Healing Spa is managed by professionals experienced in the traditional systems of Chinese therapies, slimming therapy, herbal beauty care, Taiji and other meditation courses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Villa 1183, Al Wasl Road, Dubai.<br />\r\nTel: +971 4 3483896<br />\r\nwww.naturalhealingspas.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>general@naturalhealingspas.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 4 3483896</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Villa 1183, Al Wasl Road, Dubai. www.naturalhealingspas.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '43'),
