(248, 'blue-planet-green-people--e1385232417321.jpg', 'web_restaurants.jpg', 'ZEST RESTAURANT & TAKE-AWAY', '<p>&ldquo;Zest is a healthy food concept serving natural, fresh, nutritious and delicious food and drink. We offer a menu with healthy options for breakfast, lunch, dinner and any snacks there in between.<br />\r\n&ldquo;Our products are freshly made in-house daily and we pride ourselves in using only the highest quality ingredients. Whenever possible we use organic produce. Our passion for health and all things natural means we have chosen not to mess around with mother nature. We do not use sugar, additives, preservatives or colouring. We keep our recipes simple, resulting in real honest, good, fresh food&hellip;just like you would make at home.<br />\r\n&ldquo;Our restaurant at Ibn Battuta Mall is completely open which means you get to see our kitchen, preparation, production and serving area. This is in line with a transparency we value in our company. What you see is what you get!&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Location: Tunisia Food Court, Ibn Battuta Mall.Tel: Call 800 ZEST (800 9378) for delivery.<br />\r\nwww.zest.ae</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@zest.ae</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>800 9378</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Tunisia Food Court, Ibn Battuta Mall, Jebel Ali, Dubai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '44'),
(249, '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', 'GOLDEN ENERGY HEALINGS & MEDITATION', '<p>Facilitated by Zarine, Golden Energy Healings incorporate various modalities including The Bars and Body Processes from Access Consciousness, Spiritual Healing using SRT, Theta Healing, Magnified Healing, Kinesiology, Chakra Clearings, Crystal Healing, and Sound Healing using gongs and bowls.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zarine also facilitates private, group and corporate meditation sessions incorporating guided visualizations, gonging, singing bowls and chanting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zarine can be reached at goldenenergyhealings@gmail.com or on 0506509954.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>goldenenergyhealings@gmail.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)50 650 9954</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '45'),
(250, '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', 'web_meditation.jpg', 'GEMS OF YOGA', '<p>A team of yoga instructors from different parts of India impart yoga education in different styles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A team comprising a Naturopathy Doctor, Ayurvedic Doctor and a Dietician along with male and female Ayurveda therapists provide a complete programme for body, mind and soul.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suite 1701, White Crown Building,&nbsp;Sheikh Zayed Road<br />\r\nTel: 04 3315161, 055 6532750<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/gemsofyoga\">www.facebook.com/gemsofyoga</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.gemsofyogadubai.com/\">www.gemsofyogadubai.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>gemsofyoga@live.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 331 5161</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Suite 1701, White Crown Building, between Royal Radisson Hotel &amp; Crown Plaza Hotel, Sheikh Zayed Road</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '45'),
(251, '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', 'web_hands-in-hope.jpg', 'HANDS IN HOPE MEDITATION CENTRE', '<p>By lightly touching and laying-on of hands Barbara Jackle connects with her clients. The energy begins to flow. Many clients perceive this energy as a tingling sensation or comfortable warmth. Also many people experience a feeling of lightness, security and relaxation. Also some may feel tired after finishing the session.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Barbara&rsquo;s energy also works for healthy people, they feel more fit, efficient and can feel positive differences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Originally from Germany, in Barbara&rsquo;s family, channelling abilities have been widespread for generations. &ldquo;I got my abilities as a gift and I learned to live with this precious gift in order to excel the way of supporting people throughout my grandmother&rsquo;s capacities. Her straight and honest appeal has always inspired and sensitized me.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Barbara&rsquo;s work is based on the principle of confidentiality and loyalty with regards to clients. Every word and action will be treated as highly confidential.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mobile:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;055 111 0262</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel.:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;04 351 7901</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fax.:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;04 351 7902</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@hands-in-hope.com\">info@hands-in-hope.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Address: 2nd&nbsp;floor &ndash; Office 214,&nbsp;Jumeirah Terrace Building, Jumeirah 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>P.O. Box 75590 Dubai, UAE</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hands-in-hope.com/\">www.hands-in-hope.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@hands-in-hope.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 351 7901</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>2nd floor &ndash; Office 214, Jumeirah Terrace Building, Jumeirah 1</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '45'),
(252, '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', 'vipassana-meditation-e1385234823439.jpg', 'VIPASSANA MEDITATION', '<p>Offering courses in Vipassana Meditation as taught by S.N. Goenka.&nbsp;The technique is taught at ten-day residential courses during which participants learn the basics of the method, and practice sufficiently to experience its beneficial results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The courses are run on a donation basis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information please visit the website at&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.ae.dhamma.org/\">www.ae.dhamma.org</a>&nbsp;or call&nbsp;971(0) 50 6462507 .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also send an email to&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@ae.dhamma.org\">info@ae.dhamma.org</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@ae.dhamma.org</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>050 6462507</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.ae.dhamma.org</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '45'),
(253, '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', 'tarot_private_consultation_photo-e1384723582150.gif', 'THE ALIGNMENT INSTITUTE', '<p>The aim of The Alignment Institute is to help people lead happy, harmonious and well-balanced life. We offer unique and effective solutions that focus on stress management and overall wellbeing &rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shivani Adalja is the founder of the new age well-being institute in Abu Dhabi. She offers well-being workshops, aura alignment, Feng Shui alignment, NLP private coaching, hypnotherapy, tarot workshops, &nbsp;private readings, and guided meditations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>She also offers workshops in Abu Dhabi, Dubai, Doha, Qatar, Kuwait, Thailand, and India.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information please call 0506811728.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Website :&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.shivaniadalja.com/\">http://www.shivaniadalja.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>align@shivaniadalja.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>0506811728</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>P.O. Box 114350, Abu Dhabi United Arab Emirates</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '45'),
(254, '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', 'HOLISTIC PROFESSIONAL MARIAM L. YASIN', '<p>Master Thetahealing practitioner and instructor Mariam L. Yasin conduct one &ndash; on- one sessions and facilitates certified courses in &nbsp;Thetahealing Basic DNA2 , Advanced DNA2, and Manifesting and abundance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mariam is specialised in &nbsp;Thetahealing, clinical hypnotherapy, law of attraction, EFT, reiki, pranic healing, meditation, chakra balancing, past life regression , crystal healing, color therapy, law of karma, energy healing , tarot card reading.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Individual session cost 500 AED &ndash; Package of 3 sessions cost 1250 AED. &nbsp;It&rsquo;s also possible to have the session via Skype or phone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For bookings please call 043847010 or 0506361218 or email&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@mariamyasin.com\">info@mariamyasin.com</a>. &nbsp;You can also visit her website at&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mariamyasin.com/\">www.mariamyasin.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mariam offers her services at the&nbsp;Balance Well-Being 360,&nbsp;Oasis Center, 3rd Floor Sheikh Zayed Road, Dubai.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@mariamyasin.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>043847010 / 0506361218</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Well-Being 360, Oasis Center, 3rd Floor Sheikh Zayed Road</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '45'),
