(261, 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'AWAKENED SOUL, RACHEL BEAVAN', '<p>A healer and psychotherapist, Rachel offers courses in Metaphysics including Mediumship Development, Intuitive Development, Usui Reiki Healing, Meditation, and Spiritual Healing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>She also offers one on one healing using a mix of the following modalities: Trance Communication, N.F.N.L.P Hypnotherapist, Past Life Regression, Spiritual Regression, N.L.P., Reiki, Spiritual Healing</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: beavanrachel@mac.com www.rachelbeavan.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>beavanrachel@mac.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>0000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.rachelbeavan.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '46'),
(262, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'AWAKENED POTENTIAL', '<p>Awaken Your Mind, Realise Your Potential</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dubai-based Holistic life coach Adrian Maul of Awakened Potential uses NLP, hypnotherapy and Theta to help awaken your mind and realise your potential in work, home, socialising or achieving a life goal. First session free with no-strings attached.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NLP Practitioner,<em>&nbsp;The Association for NLP</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Master Hypnotist,&nbsp;<em>California Hypnosis Institute of India</em>,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Special offer! A free consultation plus 4 x 1 hour sessions for just AED 1000, representing a saving of 50 per cent</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To find out more or book your initial consultation contact Adrian on&nbsp;056 676 9483</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>adrian@awakeningsme.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)56 676 9483</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '47'),
(263, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'RACHEL FOY HYPNOTHERAPY', '<h3>Hypnotherapy, NLP Coaching, Personal Development &amp; Life Coaching, Private Consultations, Corporate bookings &amp; Group Workshops.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Rachel provides you with tools, strategies and techniques to help you improve your life physically, mentally or emotionally. &ldquo;Maybe you are wanting to become a non-smoker or perhaps break free from food related issues, diets and counting calories.&nbsp; Or maybe you are wanting more self confidence and to be in control of your emotions, behaviour and thoughts. Or maybe you are wanting a different approach to a health condition.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rachel Foy BSc (Hons) MLCHom Dip Hyp MBIH<br />\r\nClinical &amp; Cognitive Behavioral Hypnotherapist<br />\r\nCorporate Wellness Coach</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Call the DUBAI clinic for a FREE assessment session on 04-4503525</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Located in the heart of JLT, Cluster V.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.rachelfoy.com/\">www.rachelfoy.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Check Out Rachel&rsquo;s Other Websites:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hypnobanddubai.com/\">www.hypnobanddubai.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.dubaiweightloss.com/\">www.dubaiweightloss.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.rachelfoystopsmoking.com/\">www.rachelfoystopsmoking.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hypnobirthdubai.com/\">www.hypnobirthdubai.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://ww.hypertensiondubai.com/\">ww.hypertensiondubai.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@rachelfoy.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>04-4503525</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.rachelfoy.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '47'),
(264, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'web_counselling.jpg', 'MIND BODY DYNAMIX', '<p>The mission at Mind Body Dynamix is to create harmonious families, communities, societies, countries and the world. To minimize suffering and maximize individuals innate abilities to achieve happiness and peace.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Services include executive coaching, Neuro Linguistic Programming (NLP), one to one sessions, workshops, and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MBD founder Amal Loring has counseled many UAE families on a wide range of issues ranging from social, relationship and economic matters. These experiences have produced a deep understanding of the Emirati psyche and what motivates and brings happiness to this proud and ever-changing society. Amal volunteered in a local mosque for 3 years during which time she gave many lectures on the culture of the UAE and the religion of Islam, to thousands of visitors a month. During this time she built up extensive knowledge of the culture and religion, through the inquisitive and enquiring minds of expats, tourists and foreigners to the UAE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Coupled with senior Management Coaching in a wide range of organisations both local and international gives MBD a panoramic view of issues from both perspectives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>EMAIL: info@mindbodydynamixs.com<br />\r\nTELEPHONE: +971 50 655 0438<br />\r\nFax: +971 50 655 0438<br />\r\nADDRESS: The Citadel, Business Bay,&nbsp; P.O. Box : 71947, Dubai, UAE</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.mindbodydynamixs.com/\">www.mindbodydynamixs.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@mindbodydynamixs.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 50 655 0438</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>The Citadel, Business Bay, P.O. Box : 71947, Dubai, UAE</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '47'),
(265, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_beauty.jpg', 'HEAVEN ON EARTH MED SPA', '<p>Heaven on Earth Med Spa offers&nbsp;Holistic Massage, Organic Essential Oil Aromatherapy and Hamam, Naturopathic and Natural Wellness Consultations, as well as Organic Living Foods Weight Loss &amp; Reversing Diabetes programmes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Natural Health and Wellness Consultation &ndash; AED 400 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nConsultation with Celeste Michele Roberts, American Board Certified Traditional Naturopath, Wellness and Spa Director. Learn easy ways through diet, fitness, and stress management to super charge your health and wellness. Specialty programs for: Reversing Diabetes Naturally, Weight Loss, Optimal Health and Wellness and Peak Performance in Sports Performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Private Fitness Training &ndash; AED 250 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nTrain with one of our physiotherapist in our gym to improve range of motion and performance, this training wth the physiotherapist is idea for athletes recovering from any injuries or for the person just starting on a fitness regime to ensure proper techniques in gym training and ensure safety. Private yoga, pilates, martial arts Capoeira, and fitness for pregnancy training courses also available.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Physiotherapy / Physical Therapy &ndash; AED 495 &ndash; 90 min or AED 395 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nOur expert physiotherapists will work with you to help you with your ability to move, reduce pain, restore function, and prevent disability. A wide variety of conditions are treated within this service, from low back pain to frozen shoulder, neck problems, slipped disc problems, and from headaches to ankle sprains, and knee problems. Physiotherapy can be an alternative to surgery or used to benefit before after surgeries when they are necessary for faster healing. Some specialties of our physiotherapists include: Cyriax Method, Pilates, Reflexology, Therapeutic Medical Massage, and Sports.<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.heavenonearthmedspa.com/\">www.HeavenOnEarthMedSpa.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>celeste@holistichealthonline.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0) 4 454 2806</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Concord Tower #2102, Dubai Media City, On Beach Rd. Opposite the Palm Jumeirah</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '48'),
