(271, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'web_counselling.jpg', 'MIND BODY DYNAMIX', '<p>The mission at Mind Body Dynamix is to create harmonious families, communities, societies, countries and the world. To minimize suffering and maximize individuals innate abilities to achieve happiness and peace.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Services include executive coaching, Neuro Linguistic Programming (NLP), one to one sessions, workshops, and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MBD founder Amal Loring has counseled many UAE families on a wide range of issues ranging from social, relationship and economic matters. These experiences have produced a deep understanding of the Emirati psyche and what motivates and brings happiness to this proud and ever-changing society. Amal volunteered in a local mosque for 3 years during which time she gave many lectures on the culture of the UAE and the religion of Islam, to thousands of visitors a month. During this time she built up extensive knowledge of the culture and religion, through the inquisitive and enquiring minds of expats, tourists and foreigners to the UAE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Coupled with senior Management Coaching in a wide range of organisations both local and international gives MBD a panoramic view of issues from both perspectives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>EMAIL: info@mindbodydynamixs.com<br />\r\nTELEPHONE: +971 50 655 0438<br />\r\nFax: +971 50 655 0438<br />\r\nADDRESS: The Citadel, Business Bay,&nbsp; P.O. Box: 71947, Dubai, UAE</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.mindbodydynamixs.com/\">www.mindbodydynamixs.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@mindbodydynamixs.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 50 655 0438</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>The Citadel, Business Bay, P.O. Box : 71947, Dubai, UAE</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '49'),
(272, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'web_counselling.jpg', 'ORATORSâ€™ FORUM INSTITUTE FOR HUMAN DEVELOPMENT AND BEHAVIOURAL THERAPY', '<p>Orators&rsquo; Forum uses NLP (neuro-linguistic programming) to help you take control of your mind and emotions to achieve general well-being.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>According to Orators, &ldquo;NLP sessions are designed to change one&rsquo;s way of thinking, focusing on self-esteem, power to make good decisions, direction, self-confidence, ability to create wealth, productivity, less procrastination and faster progress. It also enhances communication skills, helps develop relationships, calmness, motivation, eradicates limiting beliefs, undesirable behaviours, unreasonable fears and cravings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Orators use NLP to help combat the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Quit Smoking</li>\r\n	<li>Weight loss &ndash; virtual gastric band therapy</li>\r\n	<li>Eradicate fears, phobias, nervousness, anxiety, panic attacks</li>\r\n	<li>Overcome grief, anger, guilt, frustration, depression</li>\r\n	<li>Conquer stage fright for public speaking and professional presentations</li>\r\n	<li>Take back control from addictions, obsessions, compulsions</li>\r\n	<li>Desensitize feelings of lack and limitations, shyness, inferiority complex</li>\r\n	<li>Boost self-confidence, raise self-esteem</li>\r\n	<li>Transform to positive mental attitude</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ORATORS&rsquo; FORUM&nbsp; Institute for Human Development and Behavioural Therapy FZ-LLC</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Office #44, 3rd Floor, Block 18, Knowledge Village, Dubai, United Arab Emirates</p>\r\n\r\n<p>P.O. Box: 502221</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://wm3.eim.ae/eim/compose/compose?to=orators@eim.ae\">orators@eim.ae</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Website:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.ofi.ae/\" target=\"_blank\">www.ofi.ae</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel:&nbsp;+970-(0)55-5538295</p>\r\n\r\n<p>or +970-(0)50-7950295</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>orators@eim.ae</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+970-(0)55-5538295</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Office #44, 3rd Floor, Block 18, Knowledge Village, Dubai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '49'),
(273, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'web_counselling.jpg', 'TRANSFORMATIONS INSTITUTE', '<p>Using NLP, the Transformations team help clients increase their productivity, work and learn smarter, improve memory and concentration, resolve problems creatively, and enjoy greater confidence and self-esteem.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By combining theory and practice, revealing powerful self-awareness techniques and using state-of-the-art technologies, the TI team demonstrate how to think in open mode, stimulate and apply imagination, harness creative energy, master new skills and make the key choices necessary to transform the quality of your life and achieve your vision of success and well being. Courses include the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Individual Coaching, Counselling &amp; Therapy</li>\r\n	<li>Couples, Marital &amp; Relationship Counselling</li>\r\n	<li>Hypnobirthing</li>\r\n	<li>Parent Education &amp; Family Therapy</li>\r\n	<li>Emotional Freedom Techniques (EFT)</li>\r\n	<li>Neuro-Linguistic Programming (NLP)</li>\r\n	<li>Life &amp; Career Makeovers</li>\r\n	<li>Professional Practitioner Therapist Trainings</li>\r\n	<li>Continuing Professional Development: short courses</li>\r\n	<li>Corporate Consultancy &amp; Training</li>\r\n	<li>Stop Smoking</li>\r\n	<li>Certificate in Satir Model Counselling for Individuals, Couples &amp; Family Therapy</li>\r\n	<li>Satir Transformational Systemic Therapy &amp; Conjoint Family Therapy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>http://transforminst.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@transforminst.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 4 344 0115</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>http://transforminst.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '49'),
(274, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'TRANSFORMATIONS INSTITUTE', '<p>The Transformations Institute provides professional courses in clinical hypnotherapy , psychotherapy, counselling , EFT, NLP and much more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Our professional practitioner courses are based on holistic, humanistic and positive psychology.&nbsp;We encourage our students to adopt an eclectic approach so that they can utilise a variety of&nbsp;techniques and methodologies, including clinical and analytic hypnotherapy, transpersonal&nbsp;psychotherapy, cognitive behavioural therapy (CBT), energy and meridian therapies, and be<br />\r\nopen to any approach that enhances their professional practice in effective brief therapy and&nbsp;counselling for individuals, couples and families&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information please call &nbsp;Dr. Leila Edwards on +971 (0)50 474 5612 / +971 (0)50&nbsp;474 5613 or email&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@transforminst.com?subject=Introductory%20Workshops\" target=\"_blank\">info@transforminst.com</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also visit the website at www.transforminst.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@transforminst.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)50 474 5612</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Dubai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '49'),
(275, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'ELITE MIND SOLUTIONS', '<p>Anna Yates is a psychotherapist, clinical hypnotherapist, licensed NLP practitioner, gastric mind band therapist, pause button therapist, weight management and smoking cessation specialist.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information please call +971 (0) 506512145 / +971 (0) 44549763 or email anna@elitemindsolutions.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also visit the website at www.elitemindsolutions.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Location: Umm al Sheif Road , Umm Suqeim 1, Dubai</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>anna@elitemindsolutions.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0) 506512145 / +971 (0) 44549763</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Umm al Sheif Road , Umm Suqeim 1, Dubai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '49'),
(276, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'tarot_private_consultation_photo-e1384723582150.gif', 'THE ALIGNMENT INSTITUTE', '<p>The aim of The Alignment Institute is to help people lead happy, harmonious and well-balanced life. We offer unique and effective solutions that focus on stress management and overall wellbeing &rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shivani Adalja is the founder of the new age well-being institute in Abu Dhabi. She offers well-being workshops, aura alignment, Feng Shui alignment, NLP private coaching, hypnotherapy, tarot workshops, &nbsp;private readings and guided meditations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>She also offers workshops in Abu Dhabi, Dubai, Doha, Qatar , Kuwait , Thailand and India.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information please call 0506811728 .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Website :&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.shivaniadalja.com/\">http://www.shivaniadalja.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>align@shivaniadalja.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>0506811728</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>P.O. Box 114350, Abu Dhabi United Arab Emirates</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '49'),
(277, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'INNER SELF CONSULTANCY', '<p>Alexandra Salkova offers hypnotherapy, NLP coaching, Theta healing, EFT, Reiki, De-stress programme.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email alexandra@innerselfconsultancy.com<br />\r\nTel. 050 698 4612<br />\r\nwww.innerselfconsultancy.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>alexandra@innerselfconsultancy.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)50 698 4612</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.innerselfconsultancy.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '49'),
(278, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'AWAKENED SOUL, RACHEL BEAVAN', '<p>A healer and psychotherapist, Rachel offers courses in Metaphysics including Mediumship Development, Intuitive Development, Usui Reiki Healing, Meditation and Spiritual Healing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>She also offers one on one healing using a mix of the following modalities: Trance Communication, N.F.N.L.P Hypnotherapist, Past Life Regression, Spiritual Regression, N.L.P., Reiki, Spiritual Healing</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: beavanrachel@mac.com www.rachelbeavan.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>beavanrachel@mac.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>0000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.rachelbeavan.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '49'),
(279, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'web_holistic-ctrs.jpg', 'THE ALIGNMENT INSTITUTE', '<p>The Alignment Institute provides learning and development through life transforming workshops. The workshops empower people and initiate change in their lives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shivani Adalja has created unique workshops based on years of experience in the filed of Aura Alignment, Feng Shui Alignment and NLP. Her workshops are fun, interactive and based on unique subject matter.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to running six core workshops, we design and deliver workshops for spa and wellness industry professionals, with focus on holistic wellbeing and heightening awareness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>P.O. Box 114350, Abu Dhabi<br />\r\nTel: 050 6811728<br />\r\nEmail: align@shivaniadalja.com<br />\r\nwww.shivaniadalja.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>align@shivaniadalja.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)50 6811728</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>P.O. Box 114350, Abu Dhabi. www.shivaniadalja.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '49'),
(280, 'web_spinal_therapy.jpg', 'web_spinal_therapy.jpg', 'OSTEOPATHIC HEALTH CENTRE', '<p>Malcolm Gregory, Nargis Raza and their team of therapists, give self-help and support to people suffering from pain.<br />\r\nIssues that the Osteopathic Health Centre (OHC) can help with include back pain, neck pain, headaches, frozen shoulder, sports injuries, RSI, sinusitis, whiplash, pregnancy care, trapped nerves, tennis elbow, growing pains, postural correction, correct breathing techniques, arthritic pain, pelvic pain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Treatments include ante natal care, homeopathy, hydrotherapy, osteopathy, psychology. OHC offers rehabilitation for post-orthopedic surgery, post cardiac surgery, back pain, neck pain, post natal, sports injury, post hemiplegia (stroke)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umm Suqueim and Mirdif</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: clinicsinfo@osteopathydubai.com<br />\r\nTel: 04 348 73 66<br />\r\nwww.osteopathydubai.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>clinicsinfo@osteopathydubai.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 348 73 66</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.osteopathydubai.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '50'),
(281, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'AWAKENED POTENTIAL', '<p>Awaken Your Mind, Realise Your Potential</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dubai-based Holistic life coach Adrian Maul of Awakened Potential uses NLP, hypnotherapy and Theta to help awaken your mind and realise your potential in work, home, socialising or achieving a life goal. First session free with no-strings attached.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NLP Practitioner,<em>&nbsp;The Association for NLP</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Master Hypnotist,&nbsp;<em>California Hypnosis Institute of India</em>,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Special offer! A free consultation plus 4 x 1 hour sessions for just AED 1000, representing a saving of 50 percent</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To find out more or book your initial consultation contact Adrian on&nbsp;056 676 9483</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>adrian@awakeningsme.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)56 676 9483</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '51'),
(282, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'time-travel2-photo-courtesy-of-junussyndicate-on-deviantart-e1398866411781.jpg', 'PAST LIFE REGRESSION', '<p>Enjoy discovering your past life connections to places, people and your inner self. Member of the Past Life Therapists Association. Adv PLR &amp; LBL Specialist.<br />\r\nTo enquire or book, email Mimi on Mimi.Harding@gmail.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>Mimi.Harding@gmail.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>056 991 8852</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '51'),
(283, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'RACHEL FOY HYPNOTHERAPY', '<h3>Hypnotherapy, NLP Coaching, Personal Development &amp; Life Coaching, Private Consultations, Corporate bookings &amp; Group Workshops.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Rachel provides you with tools, strategies and techniques to help you improve your life physically, mentally or emotionally. &ldquo;Maybe you are wanting to become a non-smoker or perhaps break free from food related issues, diets and counting calories.&nbsp; Or maybe you are wanting more self confidence and to be in control of your emotions, behaviour and thoughts. Or maybe you are wanting a different approach to a health condition.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rachel Foy BSc (Hons) MLCHom Dip Hyp MBIH<br />\r\nClinical &amp; Cognitive Behavioral Hypnotherapist<br />\r\nCorporate Wellness Coach</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Call the DUBAI clinic for a FREE assessment session on 04-4503525</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Located in the heart of JLT, Cluster V.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.rachelfoy.com/\">www.rachelfoy.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Check Out Rachel&rsquo;s Other Websites:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hypnobanddubai.com/\">www.hypnobanddubai.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.dubaiweightloss.com/\">www.dubaiweightloss.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.rachelfoystopsmoking.com/\">www.rachelfoystopsmoking.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hypnobirthdubai.com/\">www.hypnobirthdubai.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://ww.hypertensiondubai.com/\">ww.hypertensiondubai.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@rachelfoy.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>04-4503525</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.rachelfoy.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '51'),
(284, 'pawn-king-shadow-e1399629806398.jpg', '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', 'HOLISTIC PROFESSIONAL MARIAM L. YASIN', '<p>Master Thetahealing practitioner and instructor Mariam L. Yasin conduct one &ndash; on- one sessions and facilitates certified courses in &nbsp;Thetahealing Basic DNA2 , Advanced DNA2, and Manifesting and abundance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mariam is specialised in &nbsp;Thetahealing, clinical hypnotherapy, law of attraction, EFT, reiki, pranic healing, meditation, chakra balancing, past life regression , crystal healing, color therapy, law of karma, energy healing , tarot card reading.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Individual session cost 500 AED &ndash; Package of 3 sessions cost 1250 AED. &nbsp;It&rsquo;s also possible to have the session via Skype or phone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For bookings please call 043847010 or 0506361218 or email&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@mariamyasin.com\">info@mariamyasin.com</a>. &nbsp;You can also visit her website at&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mariamyasin.com/\">www.mariamyasin.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mariam offers her services at the&nbsp;Balance Well-Being 360,&nbsp;Oasis Center, 3rd Floor Sheikh Zayed Road, Dubai.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@mariamyasin.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>043847010 / 0506361218</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Well-Being 360, Oasis Center, 3rd Floor Sheikh Zayed Road</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '51'),
