(314, '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', 'HOLISTIC PROFESSIONAL MARIAM L. YASIN', '<p>Master Thetahealing practitioner and instructor Mariam L. Yasin conduct one &ndash; on- one sessions and facilitates certified courses in &nbsp;Thetahealing Basic DNA2 , Advanced DNA2, and Manifesting and abundance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mariam is specialised in &nbsp;Thetahealing, clinical hypnotherapy, law of attraction, EFT, reiki, pranic healing, meditation, chakra balancing, past life regression , crystal healing, color therapy, law of karma, energy healing , tarot card reading.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Individual session cost 500 AED &ndash; Package of 3 sessions cost 1250 AED. &nbsp;It&rsquo;s also possible to have the session via Skype or phone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For bookings please call 043847010 or 0506361218 or email&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@mariamyasin.com\">info@mariamyasin.com</a>. &nbsp;You can also visit her website at&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mariamyasin.com/\">www.mariamyasin.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mariam offers her services at the&nbsp;Balance Well-Being 360,&nbsp;Oasis Center, 3rd Floor Sheikh Zayed Road, Dubai.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@mariamyasin.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>043847010 / 0506361218</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Well-Being 360, Oasis Center, 3rd Floor Sheikh Zayed Road</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '57'),
(315, '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'AWAKENED SOUL, RACHEL BEAVAN', '<p>A healer and psychotherapist, Rachel offers courses in Metaphysics including Mediumship Development, Intuitive Development, Usui Reiki Healing, Meditation and Spiritual Healing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>She also offers one on one healing using a mix of the following modalities: Trance Communication, N.F.N.L.P Hypnotherapist, Past Life Regression, Spiritual Regression, N.L.P., Reiki, Spiritual Healing</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: beavanrachel@mac.com www.rachelbeavan.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>beavanrachel@mac.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>0000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.rachelbeavan.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '57'),
(316, '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', 'web_holistic-ctrs.jpg', 'COSMIC HEALING CENTRE', '<p>Services, treatments, events and training in various healing modalities, self-empowerment workshops and meditations, plus alternative and complementary therapies. Pranic, Theta, Reiki, Vastu and Feng Shui, Crystal, KriyaShakti, EFT, Hypnotherapy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Office No: 402; Montana Building, Home Options Building, GPO, Karama, Dubai.<br />\r\nEmail: info@cosmichealingcentre.org<br />\r\nTel: 04 357 6676<br />\r\nwww.cosmichealingcentre.org</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@cosmichealingcentre.org</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 357 6676</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Office No: 402; Montana Building, Home Options Building, GPO, Karama, Dubai. www.cosmichealingcentre.org</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '57'),
