(318, '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', 'flame-of-mindfulness2.jpg', 'BREATH & HEALTH ALTERNATIVE MEDICAL CENTRE', '<p>Wellness centre offers cupping, ear candling, Aromatherapy Massage, Ayurveda, Colon Hydrotherapy, Cupping Therapy &amp; Hijama, Diet &amp; Nutrition, Ear Coning &amp; Candling, Electromagnetic Wave Therapy, Hair care (Organic), Play &amp; Creative Arts Therapy Pranic Healing, Quantum Biofeedback Therapy, Sand Tray Therapy, Stress Management, Tai Chi, Thai Massage &amp; Therapeutic Stretching, Unani,&nbsp;Yoga &amp; Fitness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Villa 1080, Al Wasl Road, Umm Suqeim 2, Dubai</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>hello@breathandhealth.net</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 348 9940</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.breathandhealth.net</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '57'),
(319, 'web_spinal_therapy.jpg', 'web_spinal_therapy.jpg', 'OSTEOPATHIC HEALTH CENTRE', '<p>Malcolm Gregory, Nargis Raza and their team of therapists, give self-help and support to people suffering from pain.<br />\r\nIssues that the Osteopathic Health Centre (OHC) can help with include back pain, neck pain, headaches, frozen shoulder, sports injuries, RSI, sinusitis, whiplash, pregnancy care, trapped nerves, tennis elbow, growing pains, postural correction, correct breathing techniques, arthritic pain, pelvic pain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Treatments include ante natal care, homeopathy, hydrotherapy, osteopathy, psychology. OHC offers rehabilitation for post-orthopedic surgery, post cardiac surgery, back pain, neck pain, post natal, sports injury, post hemiplegia (stroke)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umm Suqueim and Mirdif</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: clinicsinfo@osteopathydubai.com<br />\r\nTel: 04 348 73 66<br />\r\nwww.osteopathydubai.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>clinicsinfo@osteopathydubai.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 348 73 66</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.osteopathydubai.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '58'),
(320, 'web_spinal_therapy.jpg', 'flame-of-mindfulness2.jpg', 'SYNERGY INTEGRATED MEDICAL CENTRE', '<p><strong>Martine, Clinical Acupuncturist</strong><br />\r\nMartine (Dip. AC clin. Ac (China) Certificate in Paediatric Acupuncture) specialises in fertility, pregnancy and post-natal treatments. She uses a combination of traditional Chinese therapies including acupuncture, massage, cupping and moxibustion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dr Parviz Rashvand, Naturopathic Medicine</strong><br />\r\nDr Parviz combines natural modalities and specialises in cancer, MS, autism and other severe auto-immune and degenerative conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Andrea Tosatto, Clinical Psychologist</strong><br />\r\nSpecialising in teens and children, Dr Tosatto uses Cognitive Psychotherapy with Jungian analysis as well as yoga and music therapy as needed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: synergy8@eim.ae Tel: 04 348 5452 www.synergyctrdubai.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>synergy8@eim.ae</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 348 5452</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.synergyctrdubai.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '58'),
(321, 'web_counselling.jpg', 'web_counselling.jpg', 'MIND BODY DYNAMIX', '<p>The mission at Mind Body Dynamix is to create harmonious families, communities, societies, countries and the world. To minimize suffering and maximize individuals innate abilities to achieve happiness and peace.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Services include executive coaching, Neuro Linguistic Programming (NLP), one to one sessions, workshops, and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MBD founder Amal Loring has counseled many UAE families on a wide range of issues ranging from social, relationship and economic matters. These experiences have produced a deep understanding of the Emirati psyche and what motivates and brings happiness to this proud and ever-changing society. Amal volunteered in a local mosque for 3 years during which time she gave many lectures on the culture of the UAE and the religion of Islam, to thousands of visitors a month. During this time she built up extensive knowledge of the culture and religion, through the inquisitive and enquiring minds of expats, tourists and foreigners to the UAE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Coupled with senior Management Coaching in a wide range of organisations both local and international gives MBD a panoramic view of issues from both perspectives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>EMAIL: info@mindbodydynamixs.com<br />\r\nTELEPHONE: +971 50 655 0438<br />\r\nFax: +971 50 655 0438<br />\r\nADDRESS: The Citadel, Business Bay,&nbsp; P.O. Box : 71947, Dubai, UAE</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.mindbodydynamixs.com/\">www.mindbodydynamixs.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@mindbodydynamixs.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 50 655 0438</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>The Citadel, Business Bay, P.O. Box : 71947, Dubai, UAE</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '59'),
(322, 'web_counselling.jpg', 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'TRANSFORMATIONS INSTITUTE', '<p>The Transformations Institute provides professional courses in clinical hypnotherapy , psychotherapy, counselling , EFT, NLP and much more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Our professional practitioner courses are based on holistic, humanistic and positive psychology.&nbsp;We encourage our students to adopt an eclectic approach so that they can utilise a variety of&nbsp;techniques and methodologies, including clinical and analytic hypnotherapy, transpersonal&nbsp;psychotherapy, cognitive behavioural therapy (CBT), energy and meridian therapies, and be<br />\r\nopen to any approach that enhances their professional practice in effective brief therapy and&nbsp;counselling for individuals, couples and families&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information please call &nbsp;Dr. Leila Edwards on +971 (0)50 474 5612 / +971 (0)50&nbsp;474 5613 or email&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@transforminst.com?subject=Introductory%20Workshops\" target=\"_blank\">info@transforminst.com</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also visit the website at www.transforminst.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@transforminst.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)50 474 5612</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Dubai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '59'),
(323, 'web_counselling.jpg', 'web_baby__parents.jpg', 'DUBAI PHYSIOTHERAPY & FAMILY MEDICINE CLINIC', '<p>The Dubai Physiotherapy &amp; Family Medicine Clinic was established in 1992 to provide a fully comprehensive family medicine and physiotherapy service to the community.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The clinic provides the services of:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Family Medicine</li>\r\n	<li>Internal Medicine</li>\r\n	<li>Physiotherapy</li>\r\n	<li>Sports Therapy &amp; Rehabilitation</li>\r\n	<li>Speech Therapy</li>\r\n	<li>Acupuncture</li>\r\n	<li>Psychology</li>\r\n	<li>Chiropody / Podiatry</li>\r\n	<li>Orthotics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Hours of operation:<br />\r\nSaturday to Thursday 8am &ndash; 7pm<br />\r\nFriday closed</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Address:<br />\r\n1st Floor, Town Centre Jumeirah, Jumeirah Beach Road<br />\r\nPO Box 74638, Dubai, United Arab Emirates<br />\r\nOut of Office Hours: 24 hour answering service1st Floor, Town Centre Jumeirah, Jumeirah Beach Road, next to Mercato Mall.<br />\r\nTel: +971 (0)4 349 6333</p>\r\n\r\n<p>www.dxbphysio.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@dxbphysio.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 349 6333</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>1st Floor, Town Centre Jumeirah, Jumeirah Beach Road, Dubai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '59'),
(324, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_beauty.jpg', 'HEAVEN ON EARTH MED SPA', '<p>Heaven on Earth Med Spa offers&nbsp;Holistic Massage, Organic Essential Oil Aromatherapy and Hamam, Naturopathic and Natural Wellness Consultations, as well as Organic Living Foods Weight Loss &amp; Reversing Diabetes programmes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Natural Health and Wellness Consultation &ndash; AED 400 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nConsultation with Celeste Michele Roberts, American Board Certified Traditional Naturopath, Wellness and Spa Director. Learn easy ways through diet, fitness, and stress management to super charge your health and wellness. Specialty programs for: Reversing Diabetes Naturally, Weight Loss, Optimal Health and Wellness and Peak Performance in Sports Performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Private Fitness Training &ndash; AED 250 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nTrain with one of our physiotherapist in our gym to improve range of motion and performance, this training wth the physiotherapist is idea for athletes recovering from any injuries or for the person just starting on a fitness regime to ensure proper techniques in gym training and ensure safety. Private yoga, pilates, martial arts Capoeira, and fitness for pregnancy training courses also available.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Physiotherapy / Physical Therapy &ndash; AED 495 &ndash; 90 min or AED 395 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nOur expert physiotherapists will work with you to help you with your ability to move, reduce pain, restore function, and prevent disability. A wide variety of conditions are treated within this service, from low back pain to frozen shoulder, neck problems, slipped disc problems, and from headaches to ankle sprains, and knee problems. Physiotherapy can be an alternative to surgery or used to benefit before after surgeries when they are necessary for faster healing. Some specialities of our physiotherapists include: Cyriax Method, Pilates, Reflexology, Therapeutic Medical Massage, and Sports.<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.heavenonearthmedspa.com/\">www.HeavenOnEarthMedSpa.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>celeste@holistichealthonline.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0) 4 454 2806</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Concord Tower #2102, Dubai Media City, On Beach Rd. Opposite the Palm Jumeirah</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '60'),
(325, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_hypnotherapy.jpg', 'SJB WELLBEING', '<p>SJB wellbeing is a healing practice founded by Sharon Bland&nbsp;a Dubai-based British expert in Spiritual Trance Healing and Tibetan Usui Reiki.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sharon offers:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tibetan Usui Traditional Reiki&nbsp;</strong>(Offering healing sessions and Reiki Workshops)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Neuro Solution Orientated Kineseology&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;(Offering private sessions in balancing mind body and spirit)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Clinical Hypnotherapy&nbsp;</strong>(offering hypnotherapy for self empowerment of ones life and taking charge. Also hypnotherapy for addictions, fears &amp; Phobias)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT)</strong>&nbsp;(Healing sessions and workshops available in releasing old and unwanted emotions to facilitate to the core issue)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Access Consciousness Bars&nbsp;</strong>(Practitioner and Facilitator offering healing sessions and workshops to become a certified Access Bars Practitioner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Releasing old beliefs, patterns,behaviours and judgements)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Reflexology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kineseology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Crystal healing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chakra balancing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Jin Shin Jyutsu&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>For more information please call +971</strong></strong><strong>506847410 or send an email to&nbsp;</strong><strong><a href=\"mailto:sharon@sjbewellbeing.com\" target=\"_blank\">sharon@sjbewellbeing.com</a>. You can also visit the website at &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"http://www.sjbwellbeing.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>www.sjbwellbeing.com</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>sharon@sjbewellbeing.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971506847410</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>