(365, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_beauty.jpg', 'PASTELS SALON', '<p>Beauty: The latest beauty treatments carried out by beauty therapists and skin specialists; from waxing to semi-permanent make-up.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hair: Specializing in cutting and colouring treatments including excellent hair advice, Pastels&rsquo; hair services are about the complete works, cut, colour, advice, service and pampering.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nails: From basic manicure and pedicure to shellac, nail art, callus peel, paraffin and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Jumeirah Branch</strong><br />\r\n<strong>T&nbsp;</strong>04 388 3534/3397<br />\r\n<strong>F&nbsp;</strong>04 388 3559<br />\r\n<strong>E&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"mailto:pastels1@eim.ae\">pastels1@eim.ae</a><br />\r\n<strong>H&nbsp;</strong>Saturday to Thursday 9am &ndash; 7pm</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Ritz-Carlton Dubai Branch</strong><br />\r\n<strong>T&nbsp;</strong>04 399 5016/318 6141 &nbsp;&ndash; 052 951 5483<br />\r\n<strong>F&nbsp;</strong>04 399 5015<br />\r\n<strong>E&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"mailto:pastels2@eim.ae\">pastels2@eim.ae</a><br />\r\n<strong>H&nbsp;</strong>Seven days a week 9am &ndash; 7pm</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mercato Mall Branch<br />\r\nT&nbsp;</strong>04 344 7883<br />\r\n<strong>F&nbsp;</strong>04 344 7899<br />\r\n<strong>E&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"mailto:pastels2@eim.ae\">pastels3@eim.ae</a><br />\r\n<strong>H&nbsp;</strong>Saturday &ndash; Thursday 9am &ndash; 9pm Friday 10am &ndash; 9pm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>www.pastels-salon.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>pastels1@eim.ae</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 3883534</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Al Wasl Rd, Jumeirah</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '66'),
(366, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'REMÃˆDE SPA AT THE ST. REGIS ABU DHABI', '<p>One of UAE&rsquo;s largest spas at 3,000 square metres, the Rem&egrave;de Spa at The St. Regis Abu Dhabi offers 25 different bespoke facials, massages, body treatments, and spa packages for both ladies and gentlemen given by highly trained masseurs and aestheticians. Rem&egrave;de Spa is also the first in the UAE to offer real Oxyceutical&reg;therapies where pure oxygen is infused into the treatment to drive visible results.<br />\r\nExclusive to The St. Regis Hotels and Resorts, Rem&egrave;de Spas are found in New York, Singapore and Bali.<br />\r\nThe Rem&egrave;de Spa at The St. Regis Abu Dhabi features 11 private treatment rooms, each decorated with natural materials and earth tones as well as candles with rich aromas, plush throws, wooden floors and hand-crafted tile mosaics. The treatment rooms, wet areas, relaxation lounges and other amenities are available separately for ladies and gentlemen.<br />\r\nFor Rem&egrave;de Spa reservations, call (+971) 2 694 4758 or email remede.abudhabi@starwoodhotels.com.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>remede.abudhabi@starwoodhotels.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>(+971) 2 694 4758</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.stregisabudhabi.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '66'),
(367, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_wellness-retreat-2.jpg', 'B+WELLNESS RETREATS', '<p>Three-day retreats designed to help women jumpstart into healthy living through distressing, relaxing, and focusing on themselves and their health.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What to expect at the retreats?</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Daily health &amp; nutrition talks</li>\r\n	<li>Fitness sessions</li>\r\n	<li>Cooking workshops</li>\r\n	<li>Leisurely excursions</li>\r\n	<li>B-approved organic meals* &amp; detox juices</li>\r\n	<li>Spa services</li>\r\n	<li>Beauty &amp; Image consultation</li>\r\n	<li>Luxury amenities</li>\r\n	<li>B+Wellness gift set</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Bernadette is also available for:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>personal training &amp; small group training</li>\r\n	<li>fitness &amp; nutrition consultations</li>\r\n	<li>corporate lectures and seminars</li>\r\n	<li>school lectures &amp; health promotion programs.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Email Bernadette@bernaciseme.com<br />\r\nwww.bernaciseme.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>Bernadette@bernaciseme.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.bernaciseme.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '66'),
