(372, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'ESSENSUALS AROMATHERAPY CENTRE', '<p>Holistic women&rsquo;s spa using Decleor and Organic Neal&rsquo;s Yard Remedies products. Treatments include massages, facials, body treatments, reflexology, aroma manicure, pedicure and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>First floor, Jumeirah Centre, Jumeirah Beach Road (next to Spinneys and Magrudys).<br />\r\nEmail:essensuals1@gmail.com<br />\r\n+971 (0)4 344 8776</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>essensuals1@gmail.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 344 8776</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>First floor, Jumeirah Centre, Jumeirah Beach Road (next to Spinneys and Magrudys).</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '66'),
(373, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'NATURAL HEALING SPA', '<p>Inspired by traditional healing philosophies from China and Thailand, Natural Healing Spa embraces a holistic approach to physical and spiritual vitality.<br />\r\nLocated at the corner of Al Wasl Road, Natural Healing Spa is managed by professionals experienced in the traditional systems of Chinese therapies, slimming therapy, herbal beauty care, Taiji and other meditation courses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Villa 1183, Al Wasl Road, Dubai.<br />\r\nTel: +971 4 3483896<br />\r\nwww.naturalhealingspas.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>general@naturalhealingspas.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 4 3483896</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Villa 1183, Al Wasl Road, Dubai. www.naturalhealingspas.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '66'),
(374, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'ANAHATA SPA', '<p>Beauty, health and holistic wellbeing. Manicures with organic nail varnish and facials and body massages with healing crystals. Khalifa City A, Abu Dhabi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: +971 (0)2 557 7722<br />\r\nEmail: info@anahataspa.ae<br />\r\nwww.anahataspa.ae</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@anahataspa.ae</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)2 557 7722</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Khalifa City A, Abu Dhabi. www.anahataspa.ae</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '66'),
