(377, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'Listings_leaves-and-water.jpg', 'POINT ZERO FLOATATION CENTER', '<p>Floatation Therapy, Ayurveda and Body Works are on offer at this HAAD registered spa centre for relaxation, recuperation and rehabilitation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Khalifa City A, Abu Dhabi opposite Al Forsan Sports resort and next to Berlitz Language Center. Street #12, Villa 3.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Call +971 (2) 445 5775,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>email&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:bookings@pointzerofloatation.com\">bookings@pointzerofloatation.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>www.pointzerofloatation.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>bookings@pointzerofloatation.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (2) 445 5775</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Khalifa City A, Abu Dhabi opposite Al Forsan Sports resort and next to Berlitz Language Center. Street #12, Villa 3. www.pointzerofloatation.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '66'),
(378, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_beauty.jpg', 'SISTERS BEAUTY LOUNGE', '<p>Soothing treatments for women &ndash; massages, facials, scrubs, hair removal, reflexology, manicures and pedicures, slimming treatments, hammam, spray tan, bridal make up, eyelash and eyebrow treatments&hellip; to name some of the services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sisters Beauty Lounge carries products from The Organic Pharmacy, a leading British brand reputed to be the first and only pharmacy in the world dedicated to organic health and beauty. TOP is known for its luxurious treatments using its own specially-formulated all-natural products.<br />\r\nSisters is offering The Organic Pharmacy&rsquo;s four signature treatments, namely:<br />\r\nRose Crystal Lymphatic Facial for re-energised, glowing skin;<br />\r\nVitamin C &amp; Papaya Enzyme Peel Facial, which brightens the skin by targeting pigmentation and uneven spots;<br />\r\nSolution Facial for Combination Skin, deep-cleansing facial that leaves your skin fresh and revitalized; and,<br />\r\nBack Detox Facial, aimed at removing congestion and leave you with a smooth, deeply cleansed back.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sisters Beauty Lounge&nbsp;is located in five locations throughout the country: Al Bateen in Abu Dhabi, The Village Mall in Jumeirah, The Dubai Mall, Mirdif City Centre, and the Mall of the Emirates.&nbsp; Opening soon will be the sixth Sisters Beauty Lounge branch located in St. Regis Hotel in Abu Dhabi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@sistersbeautylounge.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 3398500</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Al Bateen in Abu Dhabi, The Village Mall in Jumeirah, The Dubai Mall, Mirdif City Centre, and the Mall of the Emirates. Opening soon will be the sixth Sisters Beauty Lounge branch located in St. Regis Hotel in Abu Dhabi. www.sistersbeautylounge.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '66'),
(379, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'web_beauty.jpg', 'KATRINA VALENTE HOLISTICS', '<p>One of the UAE&rsquo;s most respected and experience holistic beauticians, Katrina is a facial therapist and holistic aesthetician/healer with more than 20 years experience in the beauty industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For first time clients, Katrina offers a 20 per cent discount to Awakenings ME magazine readers, just tell her you&rsquo;d like to avail the &lsquo;Awakenings mag 20 per cent discount offer&rsquo; when you call or email.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>Katrina@katrinavalente.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)50 565 7679</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.katrinavalente.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '66'),
(380, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'aromatherapy1.jpg', 'ORGANIC GLOW BEAUTY LOUNGE', '<p>Eco-friendly, organic salon. Organic hair treatments, ammonia-free colour, aromatherapy massage, formaldehyde- free mani-pedis, fresh fruit facials, home- made scrubs and more. Stocks Simply Organic products for purchase.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>eco_lounge@yahoo.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0) 4 380 4666</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.organicglowuae.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '66'),
(381, 'web_beauty.jpg', 'aromatherapy1.jpg', 'SPADUNYA CLUB', '<p>Award-winning holistic and wellness spa for women using the 100 per cent organic, French colour therapy spa range called Altearah Bio in holistic vibrational and energetic treatments. Hammam, hydrotherapy, beauty room and steam, sauna and showers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Holistic Wellness Consultants offer therapies that include Reflexology, Iridology, Holistic Nutrition, Theta Healing, Quantum Reading, the Dorn Method, PIDDDS (Personal Integrated Dynamics, Diet and Determination), Breuss Massage, and Reiki.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fitness@Spadunya<br />\r\nSpadunya Club&rsquo;s fitness centre offers Personal Training, Aerobics, Pilates, Yoga, Dance, kids classes and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Therapists working out of SpaDunya Club include:<br />\r\nStephanie Niazi: Stephanie uses iridology to evaluates wellness imbalances through tissue markings in the eyes which are addressed with holistic nutrition and food solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Karima Nanji: A Dorn Method therapist, Karima offers treatment for back pain and issues stemming from the spine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shams 1, The Walk at JBR, Plaza Level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@spadunyaclub.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 439 3669</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.spadunyaclub.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '66'),
(382, 'web_yoga.jpg', 'web_yoga.jpg', 'PHOENIX RISING', '<p>Pilates, Yoga, AcroYoga, Thai Yoga Massage and Dorn Body Alignment. Various weekly locations including JBR, Jumeirah and Open Air yoga in Safa Park. See the website for details or call Sandy on +971 (0)50 735 9683 or email info@phoenix-rising.me www.phoenix-rising.me</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@phoenix-rising.me</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)50 735 9683</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.phoenix-rising.me</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '67'),
(383, 'web_yoga.jpg', 'web_spinal_therapy.jpg', 'OSTEOPATHIC HEALTH CENTRE', '<p>Malcolm Gregory, Nargis Raza and their team of therapists, give self-help and support to people suffering from pain.<br />\r\nIssues that the Osteopathic Health Centre (OHC) can help with include back pain, neck pain, headaches, frozen shoulder, sports injuries, RSI, sinusitis, whiplash, pregnancy care, trapped nerves, tennis elbow, growing pains, postural correction, correct breathing techniques, arthritic pain, pelvic pain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Treatments include ante natal care, homeopathy, hydrotherapy, osteopathy, psychology. OHC offers rehabilitation for post-orthopedic surgery, post cardiac surgery, back pain, neck pain, post natal, sports injury, post hemiplegia (stroke)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umm Suqueim and Mirdif</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: clinicsinfo@osteopathydubai.com<br />\r\nTel: 04 348 73 66<br />\r\nwww.osteopathydubai.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>clinicsinfo@osteopathydubai.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 348 73 66</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.osteopathydubai.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '67'),
(384, 'web_yoga.jpg', 'aromatherapy1.jpg', 'SPADUNYA CLUB', '<p>Award-winning holistic and wellness spa for women using the 100 per cent organic, French colour therapy spa range called Altearah Bio in holistic vibrational and energetic treatments. Hammam, hydrotherapy, beauty room and steam, sauna and showers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Holistic Wellness Consultants offer therapies that include Reflexology, Iridology, Holistic Nutrition, Theta Healing, Quantum Reading, the Dorn Method, PIDDDS (Personal Integrated Dynamics, Diet and Determination), Breuss Massage, and Reiki.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fitness@Spadunya<br />\r\nSpadunya Club&rsquo;s fitness centre offers Personal Training, Aerobics, Pilates, Yoga, Dance, kids classes and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Therapists working out of SpaDunya Club include:<br />\r\nStephanie Niazi: Stephanie uses iridology to evaluates wellness imbalances through tissue markings in the eyes which are addressed with holistic nutrition and food solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Karima Nanji: A Dorn Method therapist, Karima offers treatment for back pain and issues stemming from the spine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shams 1, The Walk at JBR, Plaza Level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@spadunyaclub.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 439 3669</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.spadunyaclub.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '67'),
(385, 'angelic-presence-1200-x-900-e1422018227863.jpg', 'angelic-presence-1200-x-900-e1422018227863.jpg', 'ANGEL LIFE COACH (ADVANCED)', '<p>Based in Abu Dhabi, Carola Becker is a Advance ANGEL LIFE COACH(R) and owner of Crystals&rsquo; Energy, a spiritual center and gift shop.<br />\r\nWhat can she do for you?&nbsp;In order to help you to grow and let go of your problems and emotional blockages that hinder you in having a happy and balanced life, Carola uses the following techniques in her&nbsp;sessions:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Angel Card Readings&nbsp;for clarification of your possibilities in the present</li>\r\n	<li>Emotional Balance with Angels (based on EB of Dr. Roy Martina) to release&nbsp;problems and trauma on a physical Level</li>\r\n	<li>Shadow Integration &ndash; an&nbsp;effective tool to come in peace with your shadow aspects</li>\r\n	<li>Shadow Process Karma and Trauma healing with Angels to let go of problems and blockages on a deep emotional and spiritual&nbsp;Level</li>\r\n	<li>Angel Trance Coaching for reprogramming your subsconscious mind</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>How can you find Carola?<br />\r\nPlease write to&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:becker_carola@hotmail.de\">becker_carola@hotmail.de</a>&nbsp;with your requests. She will answer as soon as possible to give you more information about the sessions as well as a pricing schedule. Carola gives all sessions personally face to face or via&nbsp;Skype.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Carola is certified by international ANGEL LIFE COACH &reg; Trainer Isabelle von Fallois. She also offers Angel Readings, Emotional Balance with Angels, as well as&nbsp;meridian tapping. Furthermore, she is an Advanced Angelcard Reader &trade; certified by Doreen Virtue and can give angel card readings&nbsp;via Skype or face to face.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Through her company, Crystals&rsquo; Energy, Carola also offers:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Aura sprays made of gemstones, Bach flowers, flowers, spring water</li>\r\n	<li>Essences made of flowers and spring water</li>\r\n	<li>Organic Herbal Candles</li>\r\n	<li>Waterbars made of Fairtrade Gemstones</li>\r\n	<li>Gemstone fountains</li>\r\n	<li>Gemstone lamps</li>\r\n	<li>Incense sticks</li>\r\n	<li>Jewellery ( Necklace, Bracklet, Pendants a.m.)</li>\r\n	<li>Singing Bowls</li>\r\n	<li>Feng Shui Crystals and more</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information on ANGEL LIFE COACH &reg; Training with&nbsp;Isabelle von Fallois, go to her website:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.angellifecoachtraining.com/\">http://www.angellifecoachtraining.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>becker_carola@hotmail.de</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 50 613 0911</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '68'),
(386, 'angelic-presence-1200-x-900-e1422018227863.jpg', 'WL-JPEG-by-PixelXudio-e1416404461355.jpeg', 'ATLANTEAN ENERGY HEALING', '<p>Atlantean Healing&trade; is a high vibrating energy that was used in the healing temples of Atlantis. Sessions are designed to balance the energy field as Atlanteans believed disease was a manifestation of the imbalance in the energy field. I also focus on listening to the body and its messages to find out the root causes of conditions. The energy is very high vibrational and powerful, yet it feels gentle when receiving it.<br />\r\nLOCATION Jumeirah 1<br />\r\nTEL (055) 9288477<br />\r\nEMAIL natasha@whitelotuslight.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>natasha@whitelotuslight.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>(055) 9288477</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '68'),
(387, 'angelic-presence-1200-x-900-e1422018227863.jpg', 'web_energy-healing.jpg', 'EVELIN NOVIKOVA THETAHEALING SESSIONS', '<p>To book or enquire:<br />\r\nMobile: + 971 55 947 3697<br />\r\nEmail: Evelin@thetahealingsessions.com<br />\r\nwww.thetahealingsessions.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.awakeningsme.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Evelin-Novikova-sm.jpg\"><img alt=\"Evelin Novikova sm\" src=\"http://www.awakeningsme.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Evelin-Novikova-sm-450x298.jpg\" style=\"height:298px; width:450px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>Evelin@thetahealingsessions.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 55 947 3697</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.thetahealingsessions.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '68');
INSERT INTO `holistic_posts` (`id`, `featured_img`, `post_img`, `post_name`, `post_detail`, `dir_name`) VALUES
(388, 'angelic-presence-1200-x-900-e1422018227863.jpg', 'theta-healing-final-NEW-LOGO-vertical-e1399639150697.jpg', 'AWAKENING CONFERENCES & SEMINARS ORGANIZING', '<p>ThetaHealing&reg; is the world&rsquo;s fastest growing healing modality that helps you remove your subconscious blocks allowing you to&nbsp;create instantaneous physical, mental, emotional &amp; spiritual healing. ThetaHealing&reg; is best known for the belief and feeling work, that empowers people with the ability to remove negative thoughts, emotions, feelings, traumas, phobias, abuse, curses&hellip; and replace them with positive ones. Improve your&nbsp;health, wealth, marriage, work, abundance, relationships by booking a one-on-one session or by attending a ThetaHealing&reg; seminar with Masters and Certificates of Science&nbsp;Maya Badran and Tony Shoushani of&nbsp;<em>Awakening Conferences &amp; Seminars Organizing</em>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Location: 8th&nbsp;floor, office 804, Detroit House (Sumo Sushi &amp; Blue Mart building),&nbsp;Motor City, Dubai, UAE</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto:info@awakeningthemasters.com\">info@awakeningthemasters.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.awakeningthemasters.com/\">www.awakeningthemasters.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/254200871367379/\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/254200871367379/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Awakening Conferences &amp; Seminars Organizing&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@awakeningthemasters.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 50 8491237</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '68'),
(389, 'angelic-presence-1200-x-900-e1422018227863.jpg', 'time-travel2-photo-courtesy-of-junussyndicate-on-deviantart-e1398866411781.jpg', 'PAST LIFE REGRESSION', '<p>Enjoy discovering your past life connections to places, people and your inner self. Member of of the Past Life Therapists Association. Adv PLR &amp; LBL Specialist.<br />\r\nTo enquire or book, email Mimi on Mimi.Harding@gmail.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>Mimi.Harding@gmail.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>056 991 8852</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '68'),
(390, 'angelic-presence-1200-x-900-e1422018227863.jpg', '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', 'GOLDEN ENERGY HEALINGS & MEDITATION', '<p>Facilitated by Zarine, Golden Energy Healings incorporate various modalities including The Bars and Body Processes from Access Consciousness, Spiritual Healing using SRT, Theta Healing, Magnified Healing, Kinesiology, Chakra Clearings, Crystal Healing, and Sound Healing using gongs and bowls.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zarine also facilitates private, group and corporate meditation sessions incorporating guided visualizations, gonging, singing bowls and chanting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zarine can be reached at goldenenergyhealings@gmail.com or on 0506509954.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>goldenenergyhealings@gmail.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)50 650 9954</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '68'),
(391, 'angelic-presence-1200-x-900-e1422018227863.jpg', '2638922-e1384721726332.jpg', 'NOORA DEEN RECONNECTIVE HEALING', '<p>Noora Deen is an experienced Reconnective Healing Practitioner. She does one-on-one healing sessions working with universal energy frequencies to restore balance to the body, mind, and spirit. She also facilitates The Reconnection which is a once in a life time attunement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For information on Reconnective Healing, go to www.thereconnection.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Noora can be reached at 050 400 5545 or noora.deen@live.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>noora.deen@live.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)50 400 5545</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '68'),
(392, 'angelic-presence-1200-x-900-e1422018227863.jpg', 'web_hands-in-hope.jpg', 'HANDS IN HOPE MEDITATION CENTRE', '<p>By lightly touching and laying-on of hands Barbara Jackle connects with her clients. The energy begins to flow. Many clients perceive this energy as a tingling sensation or comfortable warmth. Also many people experience a feeling of lightness, security and relaxation. Also some may feel tired after finishing the session.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Barbara&rsquo;s energy also works for healthy people, they feel more fit, efficient and can feel positive differences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Originally from Germany, in Barbara&rsquo;s family, channelling abilities have been widespread for generations. &ldquo;I got my abilities as a gift and I learned to live with this precious gift in order to excel the way of supporting people throughout my grandmother&rsquo;s capacities. Her straight and honest appeal has always inspired and sensitized me.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Barbara&rsquo;s work is based on the principle of confidentiality and loyalty with regards to clients. Every word and action will be treated as highly confidential.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mobile:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;055 111 0262</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel.:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;04 351 7901</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fax.:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;04 351 7902</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@hands-in-hope.com\">info@hands-in-hope.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Address: 2nd&nbsp;floor &ndash; Office 214,&nbsp;Jumeirah Terrace Building, Jumeirah 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>P.O. Box 75590 Dubai, UAE</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hands-in-hope.com/\">www.hands-in-hope.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@hands-in-hope.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 351 7901</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>2nd floor &ndash; Office 214, Jumeirah Terrace Building, Jumeirah 1</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n