(406, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'web_beauty.jpg', 'HEAVEN ON EARTH MED SPA', '<p>Heaven on Earth Med Spa offers&nbsp;Holistic Massage, Organic Essential Oil Aromatherapy and Hamam, Naturopathic and Natural Wellness Consultations, as well as Organic Living Foods Weight Loss &amp; Reversing Diabetes programmes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Natural Health and Wellness Consultation &ndash; AED 400 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nConsultation with Celeste Michele Roberts, American Board Certified Traditional Naturopath, Wellness and Spa Director. Learn easy ways through diet, fitness, and stress management to super charge your health and wellness. Specialty programs for: Reversing Diabetes Naturally, Weight Loss, Optimal Health and Wellness and Peak Performance in Sports Performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Private Fitness Training &ndash; AED 250 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nTrain with one of our physiotherapist in our gym to improve range of motion and performance, this training wth the physiotherapist is idea for athletes recovering from any injuries or for the person just starting on a fitness regime to ensure proper techniques in gym training and ensure safety. Private yoga, pilates, martial arts Capoeira, and fitness for pregnancy training courses also available.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Physiotherapy / Physical Therapy &ndash; AED 495 &ndash; 90 min or AED 395 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nOur expert physiotherapists will work with you to help you with your ability to move, reduce pain, restore function, and prevent disability. A wide variety of conditions are treated within this service, from low back pain to frozen shoulder, neck problems, slipped disc problems, and from headaches to ankle sprains, and knee problems. Physiotherapy can be an alternative to surgery or used to benefit before after surgeries when they are necessary for faster healing. Some specialities of our physiotherapists include: Cyriax Method, Pilates, Reflexology, Therapeutic Medical Massage, and Sports.<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.heavenonearthmedspa.com/\">www.HeavenOnEarthMedSpa.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>celeste@holistichealthonline.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0) 4 454 2806</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Concord Tower #2102, Dubai Media City, On Beach Rd. Opposite the Palm Jumeirah</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '71'),
(407, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'web_baby__parents.jpg', 'DUBAI PHYSIOTHERAPY & FAMILY MEDICINE CLINIC', '<p>The Dubai Physiotherapy &amp; Family Medicine Clinic was established in 1992 to provide a fully comprehensive family medicine and physiotherapy service to the community.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The clinic provides the services of:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Family Medicine</li>\r\n	<li>Internal Medicine</li>\r\n	<li>Physiotherapy</li>\r\n	<li>Sports Therapy &amp; Rehabilitation</li>\r\n	<li>Speech Therapy</li>\r\n	<li>Acupuncture</li>\r\n	<li>Psychology</li>\r\n	<li>Chiropody / Podiatry</li>\r\n	<li>Orthotics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Hours of operation:<br />\r\nSaturday to Thursday 8am &ndash; 7pm<br />\r\nFriday closed</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Address:<br />\r\n1st Floor, Town Centre Jumeirah, Jumeirah Beach Road<br />\r\nPO Box 74638, Dubai, United Arab Emirates<br />\r\nOut of Office Hours: 24 hour answering service1st Floor, Town Centre Jumeirah, Jumeirah Beach Road, next to Mercato Mall.<br />\r\nTel: +971 (0)4 349 6333</p>\r\n\r\n<p>www.dxbphysio.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@dxbphysio.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 349 6333</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>1st Floor, Town Centre Jumeirah, Jumeirah Beach Road, Dubai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '71'),
(408, 'web_reflexology.jpg', 'web_counselling.jpg', 'WELL WOMAN CLINIC', '<p>Psychologist Melanie Schlatter specialises in anxiety, panic attacks, depression, grief, sleep difficulties, pain, changes in body image, the initial shock of a disease or illness diagnosis, and medical treatments and tests. She also offers stress management programmes. 2nd December Street (former Al Dhiyafah Street).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: wwc@emirates.net.ae<br />\r\nTel: +971 (0)4 332 7117<br />\r\nPO Box 75859<br />\r\nwww.wellwomanclinic.ae</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>wwc@emirates.net.ae</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 332 7117</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.wellwomanclinic.ae</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '71'),
