(437, 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'web_wellness-retreat-2.jpg', 'YOGA RETREATS', '<p>Yoga classes in Dubai and group personal growth retreats worldwide.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yoga in Dubai<br />\r\nVarious locations including The Lakes, JLT<br />\r\nLivia Anzaldo, Yoga Alliance Instructor<br />\r\nEmail: livia@liv2lead.com<br />\r\nTel: 050 1819 527<br />\r\nwww.liv2lead.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Worldwide retreats<br />\r\nIncluding Nepal, Middle East, Vietnam, Sri Lanka and India, where the roots of yoga originally begun.<br />\r\nCreated by Wellness Coach &amp; Yoga Teacher Livia Anzaldo in 2010, Yoga Retreats helps individuals, companies &amp; schools to promote mind &amp; body wellbeing in various ways:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Outdoor group classes</li>\r\n	<li>In-house Wellbeing &amp; Fitness Classes</li>\r\n	<li>Classroom Training</li>\r\n	<li>Team bonding events, based on physical &amp; mental challenges</li>\r\n	<li>Short get-away &amp; breaks as employees&rsquo; Rewards or Incentives</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>T: +971 (0)50 1819527.<br />\r\nE: livia@yogaretreats.ae<br />\r\nwww.yogaretreats.ae</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>livia@yogaretreats.ae</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)50 181 9527</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.yogaretreats.ae</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '79'),
(438, 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'web_wellness-retreat-2.jpg', 'B+WELLNESS RETREATS', '<p>Three-day retreats designed to help women jumpstart into healthy living through distressing, relaxing, and focusing on themselves and their health.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What to expect at the retreats?</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Daily health &amp; nutrition talks</li>\r\n	<li>Fitness sessions</li>\r\n	<li>Cooking workshops</li>\r\n	<li>Leisurely excursions</li>\r\n	<li>B-approved organic meals* &amp; detox juices</li>\r\n	<li>Spa services</li>\r\n	<li>Beauty &amp; Image consultation</li>\r\n	<li>Luxury amenities</li>\r\n	<li>B+Wellness gift set</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Bernadette is also available for:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>personal training &amp; small group training</li>\r\n	<li>fitness &amp; nutrition consultations</li>\r\n	<li>corporate lectures and seminars</li>\r\n	<li>school lectures &amp; health promotion programs.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Email Bernadette@bernaciseme.com<br />\r\nwww.bernaciseme.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>Bernadette@bernaciseme.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.bernaciseme.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '79'),
(439, 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'web_spa_retreat.jpg', 'SIX SENSES SPA, ZIGHY BAY, OMAN', '<p>Intelligent luxury at this stunning resort that offers holistic wellness and pampering combining east and west therapies.&nbsp;Located on the northern Musandam Peninsula in the Sultanate of Oman.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: +968 2 6735 555<br />\r\nwww.sixsenses.com/sixsenseszighybay</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>enquiries-spa@sixsenses.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+968 2 6735 555</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.sixsenses.com/sixsenseszighybay</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '79'),
(440, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'IGNITE FITNESS & WELLNESS', '<p>Ignite Fitness and Wellness offer a range of fitness and wellness solutions, including military bootcamps, personal training, innovative group exercise, corporate wellness, life coaching, personal styling and nutritional advice for the individual, neighbourhood and business communities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ignite&rsquo;s Group Ex classes are guaranteed to get you stretching, lifting, toning, dancing, boxing and strengthening your way to better health and fitness. With a wide variety of styles and levels of intensity there&rsquo;s something for everyone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Classes are held throughout Dubai in all Ignite gymnasiums including the Riva Beach Club on the Palm Jumeirah, Park Place on Sheikh Zayed Road and The Shack in Umm Sequim.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Group Ex classes include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Box-Fit</li>\r\n	<li>Fit-yoga</li>\r\n	<li>ZUMBA</li>\r\n	<li>Girls Only</li>\r\n	<li>Circuits</li>\r\n	<li>Bootcamp Overhaul</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>CONTACTS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>General / Switchboard &ndash; call (+9714) 4562482 or email info@ignite-wellness.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Military Bootcamp &amp; Group Exercise &ndash; call Fabian on 055 736 4669 or email fabian@ignite-wellness.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Personal Training &ndash; call Fabian on 055 736 4669 or email fabian@ignite-wellness.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sponsorship, PR, Marketing Liz 050 104 2338 or email liz@ignite-wellness.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Corporate Wellness &ndash; call Guillaume on 050 715 0785 or email guillaume@ignite-wellness.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ignite Sport Services, Warehouse No 1, Al Manara Street, Po Box 454844, Dubai, UAE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[t]: +971 (0)4 456 2482 [f]:+971 (0)4 452 2555</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@ignite-wellness.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971(0)4) 456 2482</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.ignite-wellness.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '80'),
(441, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'Hayley-Cutler-e1399567275639.png', 'HAYLEY CUTLER KUNDALINI YOGA', '<p>Kundalini comes from the Indian word &ldquo;Kundal&rdquo; which means &ldquo;lock of hair from the beloved&rdquo;. It lies at the fourth vertebrae of the spine. The uncoiling of this hair is the awakening of the Kundalini energy; the creative potential that already exists within every human. The process of growth through Kundalini is the uncoiling of you into your original self; your true identity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kundalini means awareness, we all have this dormant energy within us which needs to be awakened and expanded if we are to reach our full potential to become fully conscious and present in life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the only Kundalini instructors in the UAE, Hayley is a Level 1 Kundalini Yoga Instructor after completing&nbsp;the 10 month Kundalini Yoga Instructor course in 2007 in London, she says to this day is &lsquo;the best thing she has ever done for her mind and body&rsquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Since 2009, Hayley has lived in Dubai&nbsp;where she&nbsp;teaches Kundalini Yoga (as per Yogi Bhajan).&nbsp;To&nbsp;get more information about where you can do a class with Hayley, go to her Facebook page at&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.awakeningsme.com/listing/hayley-cutler-kundalini-yoga/www.facebook.com/KundaliniYogaUAE\">www.facebook.com/KundaliniYogaUAE</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hayley Cutler Kundalini Yoga</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Alchemy Yoga</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>KundaliniYogaUAE@gmail.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)55 72 66970</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '80'),
(442, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_detox.jpg', 'THE WELLNESS BROTHERS', '<p>Sean and Ryan Penny are the Wellness Brothers.&nbsp;Originally from South Africa, they each hold a Masters Degree Homeopathy from the University of Johannesburg. In 2005, they relocated to Dubai with their families.<br />\r\nServices and programs include DNA testing for health, diet and fitness; the ABC of fat-loss; 10 or 15 day detox plans, and more.<br />\r\nThe wellness mission of the brothers is &nbsp;to provide effective health, weight, and performance solutions to individuals, groups, and companies. They aim to do this through<em><strong>&nbsp;</strong></em>seven individual goals:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Move more (often)</li>\r\n	<li>Eat better</li>\r\n	<li>Perform well</li>\r\n	<li>Lose weight</li>\r\n	<li>Quit smoking</li>\r\n	<li>Stress less</li>\r\n	<li>Sleep soundly</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ABOUT SEAN PENNY:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Homeopathic Practitioner &ndash; M.Tech.Hom. (SA) (Registered in SA and licensed in Dubai)</li>\r\n	<li>Homotoxicologist</li>\r\n	<li>Certified Personal Trainer</li>\r\n	<li>Co-author &ndash; something BIGGER and NO SWEAT</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>RYAN PENNY:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Homeopathic Practitioner &ndash; M. Tech. Hom. (SA) (Registered in SA)</li>\r\n	<li>Homotoxicologist</li>\r\n	<li>Clinical Nutritionist &ndash; DCN</li>\r\n	<li>Certified Personal Trainer</li>\r\n	<li>Co-author &ndash; something BIGGER and NO SWEAT</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>contactus@thewellnessbrothers.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 441 9687 to book an appt with Ryan at Optimal Fitness in Studio City, Dubai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.thewellnessbrothers.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '80'),
(443, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'GEMS OF YOGA', '<p>A team of yoga instructors from different parts of India impart yoga education in different styles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A team comprising a Naturopathy Doctor, Ayurvedic Doctor and a Dietician along with male and female Ayurveda therapists provide a complete programme for body, mind and soul.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suite 1701, White Crown Building,&nbsp;Sheikh Zayed Road<br />\r\nTel: 04 3315161, 055 6532750<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/gemsofyoga\">www.facebook.com/gemsofyoga</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.gemsofyogadubai.com/\">www.gemsofyogadubai.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>gemsofyoga@live.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 331 5161</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Suite 1701, White Crown Building, between Royal Radisson Hotel &amp; Crown Plaza Hotel, Sheikh Zayed Road</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '80'),
(444, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_beauty.jpg', 'HEAVEN ON EARTH MED SPA', '<p>Heaven on Earth Med Spa offers&nbsp;Holistic Massage, Organic Essential Oil Aromatherapy and Hamam, Naturopathic and Natural Wellness Consultations, as well as Organic Living Foods Weight Loss &amp; Reversing Diabetes programmes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Natural Health and Wellness Consultation &ndash; AED 400 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nConsultation with Celeste Michele Roberts, American Board Certified Traditional Naturopath, Wellness and Spa Director. Learn easy ways through diet, fitness, and stress management to super charge your health and wellness. Specialty programs for: Reversing Diabetes Naturally, Weight Loss, Optimal Health and Wellness and Peak Performance in Sports Performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Private Fitness Training &ndash; AED 250 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nTrain with one of our physiotherapist in our gym to improve range of motion and performance, this training wth the physiotherapist is idea for athletes recovering from any injuries or for the person just starting on a fitness regime to ensure proper techniques in gym training and ensure safety. Private yoga, pilates, martial arts Capoeira, and fitness for pregnancy training courses also available.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Physiotherapy / Physical Therapy &ndash; AED 495 &ndash; 90 min or AED 395 &ndash; 60 min</strong><br />\r\nOur expert physiotherapists will work with you to help you with your ability to move, reduce pain, restore function, and prevent disability. A wide variety of conditions are treated within this service, from low back pain to frozen shoulder, neck problems, slipped disc problems, and from headaches to ankle sprains, and knee problems. Physiotherapy can be an alternative to surgery or used to benefit before after surgeries when they are necessary for faster healing. Some specialities of our physiotherapists include: Cyriax Method, Pilates, Reflexology, Therapeutic Medical Massage, and Sports.<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.heavenonearthmedspa.com/\">www.HeavenOnEarthMedSpa.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>celeste@holistichealthonline.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0) 4 454 2806</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Concord Tower #2102, Dubai Media City, On Beach Rd. Opposite the Palm Jumeirah</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '80'),
(445, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_body-builders.jpg', 'ELIXIR SPA & HEALTH CLUB', '<p>Habtoor Grand Beach Resort &amp; Spa offers an annual membership programme that provides members with access to a comprehensive range of health, beauty and recreational services, from therapeutic spa massages and world-class tennis courts to water sports and the largest gym on Jumeirah Beach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The recreational facilities of Elixir Health Club offers members the perfect venue to get back into shape with professional coaches, four tennis courts with night lighting, two squash courts, an extensive gymnasium, beach volleyball and beach football grounds, all nestled in a luxurious beach resort.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Elixir Health Club provides private access to the main pool, Jumeriah beach and water sports such as windsurfing and water skiing for adrenaline junkies, as well as those looking to top up their tan after the winter months.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to this, members can enjoy discounted prices at Elixir Spa. With over 30 different facial and body treatments from across the globe and six treatment rooms, Elixir Spa offers Dubai residents and visitors the opportunity to rejuvenate and relax the body in a tranquil environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A full list of the benefits that a member can receive are listed below:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Elixir Spa vouchers worth AED 500 each</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pool and private beach access &ndash; includes water slides, a kid&rsquo;s pool, an outdoor Jacuzzi, a pool bar and a range of water sports</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; A complimentary dinner for two</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; A free session with the personal trainer at the gym</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 30 minutes free tennis or squash lesson</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Discounts on restaurants and bars managed by the hotel</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Discounts on spa treatments and rituals</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Discounted rates on swimming, tennis and squash lessons and personal training and fitness sessions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; A free spa hamper</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; One month of free membership upon renewal</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To become a member of Elixir Spa &amp; Health Club and gain access to the extensive amenities all year round costs AED 18 000 for women and AED 20 000 for men. For more information or to sign up to be a member, please call 04 408 4256/4260.</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>grandjumeirah@habtoorhotels.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>04 408 4256</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Habtoor Grand Beach Resort and Spa, Jumeirah Beach Residence</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '80'),
(446, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'ENGINE HEALTH & FITNESS', '<p>Engine, a metaphor for the human body&rsquo;s ability to work as efficiently as a machine, was the name created to convey movement and dynamism to Dubai&rsquo;s first stand-alone Health and Fitness facility.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Built over 3 floors Engine Health &amp; Fitness is a state of the art, 30,000 sq ft health and fitness club now open on Beach Road, Jumeirah 1. Designed while keeping the discerning member in mind, our aim has been to put the very best that exists in the world of health and fitness under one roof. And without question, provide exemplary service, meeting and exceeding member&rsquo;s expectations through our specialized group exercise classes and personal training facilities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Personal Training and Group Ex</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Personal Trainers goal at Engine Health and Fitness is to take Personal Training to a whole new level by understanding the body to a level far beyond industry standards in Dubai. We can move the body as it was designed which means that we train people safely and efficiently to help them achieve their goals, whilst minimizing risk and maximizing reward.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As you climb and sprint your way through one of our signature indoor cycling sessions which are RPM by Les Mills, you&rsquo;ll increase endurance, up your energy, burn major calories and jump-start your metabolism. With the Rolls Royce of indoor cycles, Body Bikes enhance the experience in state of the art surroundings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jump, jab, step and dance your way to a better body with our non-stop aerobic workouts. Our carefully choreographed cardio fitness classes by Les Mills will leave you toned and energized like nothing else. These include BODYCOMBAT, BODYATTACK &amp; ZUMBA.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Train, shape and strengthen with our cutting-edge conditioning classes. From core work, CXWORX, to resistance training (BODYPUMP) to high-intensity intervals, these carefully designed, comprehensive workouts build endurance and target every major muscle group while defining your body from head to toe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>GRIT</strong>&nbsp;by Les Mills is brand new to the Middle East and we are the 1st&nbsp;to offer this great class.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>Toll Free:</strong>&nbsp;800 ENGINE</strong><br />\r\nP.O. Box 894 Dubai, U.A.E.<br />\r\n<strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;+971-4-3819999<br />\r\n<strong>F:</strong>&nbsp;+971-4-3443766<br />\r\n<strong>Email:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:customercare@ehf.ae\">customercare@ehf.ae</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>www.ehf.ae</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>customercare@ehf.ae</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971-4-3819999</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Jumeirah Beach Road, Dubai</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '80'),
(447, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'TRIBEFIT GYM & CLUB', '<p><strong>TribeFit</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; is about &lsquo;<strong>Social Fitness</strong>&lsquo;, i.e., getting fit and connecting with people in a funked-out space that is not just a gym but a Club with a caf&eacute; and lounge all rolled into one.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Besides a world-class Gym, Group Exercise classes, access to a range of team Sports facilities, inspirational Personal Training, &nbsp;Beach Bootcamps, and in-club DJs, TribeFit also has a packed Social Calendar with activities like monthly Parties, Brunches, Coffee Mornings and Evenings, Movie Nights, Networking Events, outdoor Camping Trips and more, designed to get members mixing and talking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Work out, get introduced, create friendships, meet people, or even fall in love with people who have a common interest in fitness, socially active living, and having fun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All you have to do is show up, plug in and play. The Tribe takes care of the rest.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Call the Tribe on&nbsp;<strong>800 TRIBE (87423)</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If it matters to you, it matters to us. Email us on<strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@tribefit.com\">info@tribefit.com</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Silverene Tower in Dubai Marina.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Directions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Silverene Tower is located right next to Dubai Marina Mall (when driving in the direction from Dubai to Abu Dhabi). TribeFit is on the entire Mezzanine and Ground floor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TribeFit is above Carrefour Supermarket. You can also access TribeFit from Marina Walk.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>http://www.tribefit.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@tribefit.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>800 TRIBE (87423)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Silverene Tower in Dubai Marina</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '80'),
(448, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_yoga.jpg', 'GEMS OF YOGA', '<p>This yoga studio&nbsp;&nbsp;housed in an apartment, has a hippie vibe and focuses on teaching old-fashioned yoga to eager students who sing their praises. Their hatha and traditional ashtanga yoga classes are popular, but for a more intense experience, try a session of power yoga. Gems of Yoga also facilitates yoga teacher training. For more information please call 043315161 or visit their website www.gemsofyogadubai.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@gemsofyogadubai.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>043315161</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Suite 1701, White Crown Building, Sheikh Zayed Road, 37301, Dubai, UAE</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '80'),
(449, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_yoga.jpg', 'YOGA ROOM, JLT', '<p>This Ashtanga yoga studio welcomes the new and the seasoned, the young and the old, and people from any walk of life to come in and experience Ashtanga yoga in its truest and purest form as it was originally taught by Sri K. Pattabhi Jois, father of this method.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Swiss Tower, Cluster Y, JLT.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel. +971(0)50 518 9966<br />\r\nEmail: info@yogaroom.ae<br />\r\nwww.yogaroom.ae</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@yogaroom.ae</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971(0)50 518 9966</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Swiss Tower, Cluster Y, JLT</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '80'),
(450, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_yoga.jpg', 'RAWR BIKRAM YOGA DUBAI', '<p>Rawr Yoga is a Bikram Yoga Specialised Studio, a place where you can eat, drink, work, relax, socialise and of course practice this magical type of yoga.<br />\r\n&ldquo;We wanted to share our passion for yoga by creating an inspiring space &ndash; one that we hope you&rsquo;ll want to hang out in and enjoy long after your class has finished.<br />\r\n&ldquo;With clean modern lines and a stylish interior, the 4100sqft Rawr Yoga studio is located in the heart of Dubai Media City with views of the Arabian sea and the city&rsquo;s landmarks.<br />\r\n&ldquo;Our Teachers, each of them certified personally by Bikram Choudhury, come from all over the world and teach with love, compassion and wit, ensuring the highest quality instruction and a safe, enjoyable environment.<br />\r\n&ldquo;Don&rsquo;t worry if you can&rsquo;t touch your toes. We couldn&rsquo;t either when we started, just come and Rawr&rsquo;rrr with us.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Al Sufouh Rd, 713 Concord Tower, Dubai Media City (same building as Lime Tree cafe and Mini Cooper showroom)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: info@rawryoga.com<br />\r\nTel: +971 (0)4 4232 808<br />\r\nwww.rawryoga.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@rawryoga.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 4232 808</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>Al Sufouh Rd, 713 Concord Tower, Dubai Media City (same building as Lime Tree cafe and Mini Cooper showroom)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '80'),
(451, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_yoga.jpg', 'PHOENIX RISING', '<p>Pilates, Yoga, AcroYoga, Thai Yoga Massage and Dorn Body Alignment. Various weekly locations including JBR, Jumeirah and Open Air yoga in Safa Park. See the website for details or call Sandy on +971 (0)50 735 9683 or email info@phoenix-rising.me www.phoenix-rising.me</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@phoenix-rising.me</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)50 735 9683</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.phoenix-rising.me</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '80'),
(452, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_yoga.jpg', 'IRINA YOGA', '<p>Private and group Hatha Yoga at venues across Dubai with Irina Sharma.<br />\r\nPersonal sessions based upon what every individual in the session needs for their unique circumstances regarding their body posture, mind, energy, and injury and/or limitations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email: info@irinayoga.org<br />\r\nwww.irinayoga.org</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@irinayoga.org</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>0000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Address</th>\r\n			<td>www.irinayoga.org</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '80'),
(453, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_wellness-retreat-2.jpg', 'YOGALATES BLISS', '<p>Yogalates (fusion of Yoga &amp; Pilates) at Fraser Suites, Noura El-Imam hosts Yoga Workshops and Teacher Trainings as well as Adventure &amp; Wellness Retreats.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: +971 (0)50 3289 642<br />\r\nwww.yogalatesblissindubai.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>yogalatesdxb@gmail.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)50 3289 642</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '80'),
(454, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_body-builders.jpg', 'MMA FITNESS CENTRE', '<p>Hot yoga is held at this multi-discipline fitness centre.<br />\r\nMMA Fitness Centre enables everyone to enjoy the fusion of disciplines, known as Mixed Martial Arts.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Fitness and good health</li>\r\n	<li>Confidence, mental strength and discipline</li>\r\n	<li>Self-defence for the real world</li>\r\n	<li>Lifelong friendships</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Location: Pacific Bldg. 2nd Level, TECOM, Dubai, UAE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: +971 (0)4 367 5077<br />\r\nEmail: info@mmafitcenter.com<br />\r\nwww.mmafitcenter.com</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@mmafitcenter.com</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 367 5077</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '80'),
(455, 'web_gym-exercise.jpg', 'web_yoga.jpg', 'FITNESS 360', '<p>Fitness 360 offers a range of fitness products and gives choices to its members on how they wish to incorporate fitness into their schedules. Be it exercising, assistance in weight loss or guidance to make healthy decisions &ndash; it works on the belief that everyone has the inherent ability to become fit and feel great on they&rsquo;re own individual terms.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Every branch is built uniquely based on location and the needs of the neighbourhood. Our concepts range from a full-fledged health club to an express club and most importantly the first ladies only club that offers top of the line facilities for women only. These tailor-made clubs are essentially a first in the region re enforcing our belief that fitness must be based on individual needs. By providing state-of-the-art facilities and highly trained professionals, we work closely with our members to help them achieve their goals. This is what defines our quality at Fitness 360.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Four locations across Dubai.<br />\r\n<strong>Arabian Center&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\nLocated Ground Floor.<br />\r\nAl Khawaneej Road in Mirdif,<br />\r\nbetween Dubai Royal School and Dubai Modern School.<br />\r\nLandline: +971 (0)4 236 2111</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mazaya Centre</strong><br />\r\nMezzanine, Mazaya Centre ( Near Homes R Us)<br />\r\nSheikh Zayed Rd., Dubai<br />\r\nNear Dubai Metro Station ( Dubai Mall Station, Business Bay Side)<br />\r\nLandline: 04 3307711</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>International City</strong><br />\r\nShops 05 &ndash; 10<br />\r\nChina Cluster, D-1, Al Warsan Area<br />\r\nInternational City, Phase &ndash; 1<br />\r\nDubai U.A.E.<br />\r\nLandline: 04315178</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email info@fitness360.me<br />\r\nwww.fitness360.me</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Email Address</th>\r\n			<td>info@fitness360.me</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Phone number</th>\r\n			<td>+971 (0)4 236 2111</t